{"type":"message","id":"b882282d","parentId":"ecff4bfa","timestamp":"2026-04-17T12:33:05.572Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants my plan. Let me think about the comprehensive fix strategy.\n\nBased on my deep analysis:\n\n**Root Cause Chain:**\n1. The v8 Router (3102) was never built/deployed - it's referenced everywhere but doesn't exist\n2. openclaw-listener is configured to connect to non-existent 3102 - it's idle/wasted\n3. context-api conflicts on port 3106 with listener's health endpoint - crashing in loops\n4. session-summary hook can't work because it needs to call LLM via 3102 (v8 Router)\n5. Three-layer memory is broken at layer 2 (session-summary)\n\n**Key Decision Points:**\n\n\nThe Gateway runs on 18789 while the old documentation specified 3100, and the v8 Router was supposed to be a Node.js service on 3102 that provided both intent detection and scoring endpoints. However, only the scoring component on 3103 actually exists - the intent detection and routing logic never got implemented. The hooks were written expecting this v8 Router to exist, so they're all failing because they're trying to call endpoints that were never built.\n\nLooking at the listener configuration, it's hardcoded to connect to 3102 for both the Gateway WebSocket and the API endpoints. I need to figure out whether to build the missing v8 Router service, route traffic differently, or update the listener to use the actual 3103 endpoint instead.\n\nThe cleaner approach is to fix the listener configuration to point to the real services—18789 for the Gateway and 3103 for scoring—rather than trying to recreate an entire middleware service. I should also resolve the port conflict on 3106 where context-api and the listener's health server are colliding, then verify the hook chain is functioning end-to-end.\n\nFor the remaining issues, I'll need to sort out the Feishu authentication problem with wiki-learn and look at whether the context-api actually belongs in this setup or if it's redundant.","thinkingSignature":"0618651a603e992e245c38e23036a9f117c711f4d236a2f0655b027fa72fdee7"},{"type":"text","text":"## 修复方案\n\n---\n\n### 核心判断：不要重建不存在的服务，而是让现有组件各司其职\n\n3102 v8Router 从来没有部署过。旧文档描述的架构是\"理想状态\"，实际部署时只有：\n- **3103**: v8 scoring（Node.js 服务，真实存在）\n- **3105**: scene classifier（Python 服务，真实存在）\n- **18789**: Gateway（真实存在）\n\n所有 hook 都在等一个不存在的 3102，这是一开始就埋下的架构错配。\n\n---\n\n### 分三步走\n\n#### 🔧 第一步：止血（5分钟）\n\n| 操作 | 原因 |\n|------|------|\n| **停用** `openclaw-context-api.service` | 端口冲突，crash loop 5111次，完全冗余 |\n| **修复** `openclaw-listener/config.json` | gateway.ws → `18789`，去掉 intent/score 调用（或者注释掉这段逻辑） |\n| **重启** listener | 使配置生效 |\n\n#### 🔧 第二步：修复记忆链路（10分钟）\n\n| 操作 | 原因 |\n|------|------|\n| **改造** `session-summary/handler.js` | 不再依赖 3102，改用直接调用 LLM API（通过 minimax/deepseek provider） |\n| **验证** ephemeral 写入 → session-summary 生成 → bootstrap 读取 全链路 | 跑一个 `/new` 测试 |\n| **修复** `wiki-learn` cron 的 401 认证 | 检查 Feishu API key 配置 |\n\n#### 🔧 第三步：验证完整性（5分钟）\n\n| 操作 | 原因 |\n|------|------|\n| 跑 `/new` 后观察是否有\"根据上次记忆\"提示 | 这是 bootstrap 成功的标志 |\n| 检查 `memory/` 是否有新的 session-summary | 验证 session-summary hook 是否正常 |\n| 对比 cron 任务状态 | 确认没有报错的任务 |\n\n---\n\n### 关键风险预警\n\n1. **修改 listener 配置后**，如果 gateway token 不对，listener 可能连不上 gateway。需要确认 `openclaw-listener/config.json` 里的 `token` 和 gateway 的 auth token 一致。\n2. **session-summary hook 改造**涉及改写 `handler.js`，如果 LLM API 调用失败需要有降级（写规则摘要）。\n3. **context-api 停用后**，如果 `context-api/index.js` 有其他被依赖的地方需要先确认。\n\n---\n\n**要我从第一步开始执行吗？** 还是你有其他优先级？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58,"output":916,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":52484,"totalTokens":75096,"cost":{"input":0.0000174,"output":0.0010992,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0.0196815,"total":0.022096380000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776429149466,"responseId":"06315b5b62792a34846a9e1963ec331c"}}
