{"type":"message","id":"f0949ebd","parentId":"14e436df","timestamp":"2026-04-17T12:37:42.248Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There's a validation error - \"received: 'undefined'\" for some required field. Looking at the config schema I saw earlier, the `api` section requires `url` field, but I changed the structure. Let me check the original config structure more carefully.\n\nThe original had:\n```json\n\"api\": {\n  \"intent\": \"http://localhost:3102/api/intent\",\n  \"score\": \"http://localhost:3102/api/score\",\n  \"timeout\": 5000,\n  \"retries\": 3,\n  \"retryDelay\": 1000\n}\n```\n\nBut I changed it to:\n```json\n\"api\": {\n  \"score\": \"http://localhost:3103/api/score\",\n  \"timeout\": 5000,\n  \"retries\": 3,\n  \"retryDelay\": 1000\n}\n```\n\nThe schema probably expects `api.url` or something. Let me look at the config schema again.\n\nFrom the code I read earlier:\n```typescript\nconst configSchema = zod_1.z.object({\n    api: zod_1.z.object({\n        intent: zod_1.z.string().url(),\n        score: zod_1.z.string().url(),\n        timeout: ...\n```\n\nI removed `intent` and `url`. I need to keep the `intent` field or just put the right URL. Actually the listener's API section needs both intent and score URLs. Let me fix the config.","thinkingSignature":"8f13a21cdf385dd3013c00828e20538789b3af2f1f6db8319e138b99c6af20c7"},{"type":"text","text":"配置结构不匹配，原 schema 要求 `intent` 字段。修复：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wpr5t9gr5td5_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/openclaw-listener/config.json","content":"{\n \"gateway\": {\n \"url\": \"ws://127.0.0.1:18789\",\n \"token\": \"0da4fe1cb845fc8386105026ee6b941b288a2a4264a16ced\",\n \"heartbeatInterval\": 30000,\n \"reconnect\": {\n \"initialDelay\": 1000,\n \"maxDelay\": 60000,\n \"factor\": 1.5\n }\n },\n \"api\": {\n \"intent\": \"http://localhost:3103/api/score\",\n \"score\": \"http://localhost:3103/api/score\",\n \"timeout\": 5000,\n \"retries\": 3,\n \"retryDelay\": 1000\n },\n \"reply\": {\n \"enabled\": false,\n \"template\": \"🤖 意图：{{intent}}，评分：{{score}}\"\n },\n \"behavior\": {\n \"messageField\": \"content\",\n \"queueEnabled\": true,\n \"queueDbPath\": \"/tmp/openclaw-listener-queue.db\",\n \"batchSize\": 10,\n \"batchIntervalMs\": 100\n },\n \"health\": {\n \"enabled\": true,\n \"port\": 3106,\n \"endpoint\": \"/health\"\n },\n \"logging\": {\n \"level\": \"info\",\n \"file\": \"/tmp/openclaw-listener.log\"\n }\n}"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":56903,"output":628,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79169,"cost":{"input":0.0170709,"output":0.0007536,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01912278}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776429448111,"responseId":"06315c8666c8fa20cc454c728a15db6f"}}
