{"type":"message","id":"da3230d0","parentId":"14d92f02","timestamp":"2026-04-17T12:39:01.733Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_li51xkpfjaji_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 实际使用时替换为真实密钥\nMINIMAX_API_KEY=your-actual-minimax-key\nDEEPSEEK_API_KEY=your-actual-deepseek-key\nCLASSIFIER_CACHE_TTL=300\nROUTING_LOG_ENABLED=true---\n<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n---\nv8Client.js"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":362,"aggregated":"# 实际使用时替换为真实密钥\nMINIMAX_API_KEY=your-actual-minimax-key\nDEEPSEEK_API_KEY=your-actual-deepseek-key\nCLASSIFIER_CACHE_TTL=300\nROUTING_LOG_ENABLED=true---\n<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n---\nv8Client.js","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776429541670}}
{"type":"message","id":"f3621f2e","parentId":"da3230d0","timestamp":"2026-04-17T12:39:05.082Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The .env file has placeholder keys! So the actual Minimax API key is NOT in the .env file. It must be in the auth-profiles.json or somewhere else.\n\nThe gateway doesn't expose a direct HTTP API for chat completions on the web root.\n\nLet me look at the proxy's v8Client.js to understand how it calls the LLM.","thinkingSignature":"60d40f33036c170a2f03f32acb5005364067e52ffdf63c11ef06b68bf26e0c48"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jk9s0es2lhwv_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/proxy/clients/v8Client.js","limit":50}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":67178,"output":123,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88939,"cost":{"input":0.0201534,"output":0.00014759999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02159928}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776429541735,"responseId":"06315ce4c2d3df2078b6991ba5695820"}}
{"type":"message","id":"58b89ff3","parentId":"f3621f2e","timestamp":"2026-04-17T12:39:05.427Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_jk9s0es2lhwv_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"const axios = require('axios');\n\nconst CLASSIFIER_URL = process.env.CLASSIFIER_URL || 'http://localhost:3104/classify';\nconst SCORER_URL = process.env.SCORER_URL || 'http://localhost:3103/api/score';\nconst CLASSIFIER_TIMEOUT = parseInt(process.env.CLASSIFIER_TIMEOUT || '300');\nconst SCORER_TIMEOUT = parseInt(process.env.SCORER_TIMEOUT || '2000');\n\nlet circuitOpen = false;\nlet failureCount = 0;\nconst CIRCUIT_THRESHOLD = 3;\n\nconst TASK_SCENES = new Set(['task_multi_step', 'high_risk_automated', 'fault_recovery', 'task_status_query', 'cancel_task', 'clarify', 'vague_request']);\n\nfunction fallbackClassify(text) {\n  const lower = text.toLowerCase();\n  const taskPatterns = [/运行|执行|构建|测试|部署|编译|安装|创建|删除|修改|重构|分析|检查|修复/, /帮我|请|做|写|生成|优化/];\n  const isTask = taskPatterns.some(p => p.test(lower));\n  let scene = 'default';\n  if (/天气|你好|谢谢|笑话/.test(lower)) scene = 'chitchat';\n  else if (/起不来|挂了|报错|失败|恢复/.test(lower)) scene = 'fault_recovery';\n  else if (isTask) scene = 'task_multi_step';\n  return { isTask, confidence: 0.6, scene, source: 'fallback' };\n}\n\nfunction fallbackScore(prompt) {\n  const lower = prompt.toLowerCase();\n  let score = 30, strategy = 'DIRECT', timeout = 60;\n  if (/重构|编译|构建|测试|部署/.test(lower)) { score = 45; strategy = 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT'; timeout = 180; }\n  return { score, factors: {}, recommendedStrategy: strategy, timeout, source: 'fallback' };\n}\n\nasync function classify(text) {\n  if (circuitOpen) return fallbackClassify(text);\n  try {\n    const response = await axios.post(CLASSIFIER_URL, { text }, { timeout: CLASSIFIER_TIMEOUT });\n    const data = response.data;\n    const scene = data.scene || 'default';\n    failureCount = 0;\n    return { isTask: TASK_SCENES.has(scene), confidence: data.confidence ?? 0.5, scene, meta: data.meta, source: 'classifier' };\n  } catch (err) {\n    failureCount++;\n    if (failureCount >= CIRCUIT_THRESHOLD) circuitOpen = true;\n    return fallbackClassify(text);\n  }\n}\n\nasync function score(prompt, context = {}) {\n  try {\n    const response = await axios.post(SCORER_URL, { prompt, context }, { timeout: SCORER_TIMEOUT });\n    const data = response.data;\n\n[7 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776429545363}}
{"type":"message","id":"ed3cbf85","parentId":"58b89ff3","timestamp":"2026-04-17T12:39:18.424Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is the proxy's v8Client, which is used by the proxy to call the classifier and scorer. But it doesn't have a chat/completion method.\n\nOK, let me take a step back. The session-summary hook needs to call an LLM for generating summaries. The most practical options are:\n\n1. **Direct Minimax API call** - but I don't have the API key\n2. **Direct codingplan API call** - the API key is `J99ouXWKXO8Zg5tLqv92YVsPNFhwuZc-z6z2ioeg7VE`, baseUrl is `https://zhenze-huhehaote.cmecloud.cn/api/coding/v1`\n\n\n3. **Use the task orchestrator skill** - there's a `scripts/wiki-learn-once.sh` that handles similar LLM calls\n\nI'm realizing the real issue: the hook needs to call an LLM API, but I'm missing the actual API key for Minimax. The codingplan API key works with the proxy, but that routes through the proxy which connects to 3102 (non-existent), so that won't help either.\n\nI could try calling Minimax directly since the API key is in the config, but that key turned out to be a placeholder. Let me check if there's a `.env` file in the v8 directory or if the key is set as an environment variable elsewhere.\n\nActually, the most straightforward fix is to have the session-summary hook invoke the `wiki-learn-once.sh` script directly instead of trying to make its own LLM API call.","thinkingSignature":"7cd3f33657fa71fdc4767bdbd8b5bc81a06978aa327e5fb4192a8f6305d092b4"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_932nysrhez3a_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-learn-once.sh 2>/dev/null | head -30\necho \"---\"\n# Also check if there's an LLM API available in the environment\nenv | grep -i \"MINIMAX\\|DEEPSEEK\\|API_KEY\" 2>/dev/null | grep -v \"your-actual\" | head -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":67938,"output":425,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90001,"cost":{"input":0.020381399999999997,"output":0.0005099999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.022189679999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776429545429,"responseId":"06315ce9c19d7c89a6ee8cca76c2c1f7"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0b2b7173","parentId":"ed3cbf85","timestamp":"2026-04-17T12:39:18.881Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_932nysrhez3a_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/bin/bash\n# Wiki Auto-Learn 单次执行脚本\n# 配合 cron 使用，每小时触发一次\n#\n# 策略：\n#   1. 只摄入新 skill（不在 entities/ 且不在 blocklist/ 中）\n#   2. blocklist 防止被删的 entity 重复摄入\n#   3. 有空间才添加，超标才 prune\n\nWORKSPACE=\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace\"\nENTITIES=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/entities\"\nRAW=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/raw\"\nLOG=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/log.md\"\nSKILLS_DIR=\"$WORKSPACE/skills\"\nARCHIVE=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/entities-archive\"\nBLOCKLIST=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/.wiki-learn-blocklist\"  # 被删除的 skill 名列表\n\nTARGET=28\nBUFFER=3\n\nmkdir -p \"$RAW/docs\" \"$RAW/papers\" \"$RAW/notes\" \"$ARCHIVE\"\n\necho \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] === wiki-learn-once 启动 ===\"\n\n# ===== 辅助：计算可丢弃分数（越小越先删）=====\ndisposability_score() {\n    local f=$1\n    local score\n    if grep -q \"status: auto-ingested\" \"$f\" 2>/dev/null; then\n        score=0\n---\nOPENCLAW_SERVICE_MANAGED_ENV_KEYS=CLASSIFIER_CACHE_TTL,DEEPSEEK_API_KEY,MINIMAX_API_KEY,ROUTING_LOG_ENABLED"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":235,"aggregated":"#!/bin/bash\n# Wiki Auto-Learn 单次执行脚本\n# 配合 cron 使用，每小时触发一次\n#\n# 策略：\n#   1. 只摄入新 skill（不在 entities/ 且不在 blocklist/ 中）\n#   2. blocklist 防止被删的 entity 重复摄入\n#   3. 有空间才添加，超标才 prune\n\nWORKSPACE=\"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace\"\nENTITIES=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/entities\"\nRAW=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/raw\"\nLOG=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/log.md\"\nSKILLS_DIR=\"$WORKSPACE/skills\"\nARCHIVE=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/entities-archive\"\nBLOCKLIST=\"$WORKSPACE/memory/.wiki-learn-blocklist\"  # 被删除的 skill 名列表\n\nTARGET=28\nBUFFER=3\n\nmkdir -p \"$RAW/docs\" \"$RAW/papers\" \"$RAW/notes\" \"$ARCHIVE\"\n\necho \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] === wiki-learn-once 启动 ===\"\n\n# ===== 辅助：计算可丢弃分数（越小越先删）=====\ndisposability_score() {\n    local f=$1\n    local score\n    if grep -q \"status: auto-ingested\" \"$f\" 2>/dev/null; then\n        score=0\n---\nOPENCLAW_SERVICE_MANAGED_ENV_KEYS=CLASSIFIER_CACHE_TTL,DEEPSEEK_API_KEY,MINIMAX_API_KEY,ROUTING_LOG_ENABLED","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776429558773}}
{"type":"message","id":"e0b4211e","parentId":"0b2b7173","timestamp":"2026-04-17T12:39:36.521Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The `MINIMAX_API_KEY` and `DEEPSEEK_API_KEY` are listed as `OPENCLAW_SERVICE_MANAGED_ENV_KEYS`, meaning they are managed by the OpenClaw service. They are NOT in the .env file as actual values - the .env file has placeholders.\n\nLet me think about the best approach here:\n\n1. The session-summary hook needs LLM access\n2. It currently tries to call `http://127.0.0.1:3102/v1/chat/completions` which doesn't exist\n3. I can't easily call the Minimax API directly because I don't have the API key\n\n\n4. The codingplan API at `https://zhenze-huhehaote.cmecloud.cn/api/coding/v1` with key `J99ouXWKXO8Zg5tLqv92YVsPNFhwuZc-z6z2ioeg7VE` should work, though there's a mismatch: the handler references `minimax/MiniMax-M2.7` but the codingplan only has `minimax-m2.5` available.\n\nI could try using the Gateway's WebSocket command API instead, but that's getting complicated. A simpler fix would be to make the session-summary hook call the LLM directly through the codingplan API or modify the handler to use whatever model is actually available. the handler.js to:\n1. Call the codingplan API with `minimax-m2.5`\n2. Or call the minimax API if I can figure out the key\n\nBut actually, I realize I can use the `curl` command to test the codingplan API. Let me try it first.\n\nActually, wait. Let me re-think the approach. The session-summary hook runs inside the gateway process (as part of the hook system). It has access to the filesystem and can make HTTP requests.\n\nThe simplest fix that will definitely work:\n- Change the LLM endpoint from `3102` (non-existent) to the codingplan API URL\n- Use the correct model `minimax-m2.5`\n\nBut I need to verify the codingplan API actually works first. Let me test it.\n\nActually, I realize there's another option: use `http://127.0.0.1:3103/api/score` for scoring (it's working), but that's a scoring API, not a chat API. That won't help for generating summaries.\n\nThe most straightforward solution is to call the codingplan API directly from the handler. Let me test whether this API endpoint actually works.","thinkingSignature":"036065b34b33a3de97f670792d65fa1e4250d6de591007c675877f9e41ef5f76"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_168hxrlkwqq4_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Test codingplan API directly\ncurl -s -X POST \"https://zhenze-huhehaote.cmecloud.cn/api/coding/v1/chat/completions\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer J99ouXWKXO8Zg5tLqv92YVsPNFhwuZc-z6z2ioeg7VE\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"model\": \"minimax-m2.5\",\n    \"messages\": [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"Say hello in one word\"}],\n    \"max_tokens\": 10\n  }' 2>&1 | head -5"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":68693,"output":695,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91026,"cost":{"input":0.0206079,"output":0.000834,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02274018}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776429558884,"responseId":"06315cf585f9839dd54637c663052b72"}}
