{"type":"message","id":"3b53c23e","parentId":"7e034e9a","timestamp":"2026-04-17T12:43:10.811Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"User chose option A - wait for natural /new. They also reminded me to think step by step before each action.\n\nSince they're choosing A, I should acknowledge and explain what will happen at the next natural /new, without taking any destructive actions.\n\nLet me think about what the user needs:\n1. They chose A (wait for natural /new)\n2. They want me to think before each step\n\nSince no action is being taken now (waiting for natural /new), I should:\n1. Confirm what we accomplished\n2. Explain what will happen automatically at next /new\n3. Explain the success criteria\n4. Ask if they want to proceed to step 4 (wiki-learn fix) in the meantime\n\n\n5. Step 4 involves diagnosing the wiki-learn 401 error by examining the wiki-auto-learn.py script and its authentication configuration, which I can do without risking any state loss.","thinkingSignature":"c2f633b326ca2e30965e28aff8d24b2e7b1126db5478a689b6cd44aacef95d54"},{"type":"text","text":"<thinking>\n### 1. 需求拆解\n用户选择 A（等自然 /new 验证）。当前不需要执行任何破坏性操作。可以告知结果，并询问是否在等待期间处理步骤4（wiki-learn 401 修复）。\n\n### 2. 方案推演\n**当前应做的事**：\n- 确认步骤1-2的最终状态\n- 说明下次 /new 时观察什么\n- 可选：执行步骤4（wiki-learn 401诊断），这不需要 /new，是独立操作\n\n**步骤4分析**：\n- wiki-learn cron 报错：HTTP 401 = 认证失败\n- 原因可能是 Feishu API secret key 格式/位置/携带方式有问题\n- 需要查看 wiki-auto-learn.py 的认证代码\n\n### 3. 自我质疑\n- 用户没有要求执行步骤4，我应该等用户明确要求再动\n- 用户提醒了\"执行每一步先必须进行思考\"，说明他们希望我在每个回复前都先思考\n\n### 4. 最终决策\n给出步骤1-2完成确认 + 下次 /new 观察指南。不主动执行步骤4，除非用户要求。\n</thinking>\n\n好。步骤1-2已稳定完成，当前无需操作。\n\n---\n\n**下次自然 /new 时观察两点：**\n\n1. 新 session 回复开头是否有\"根据上次 session 的记忆...\"提示（→ bootstrap 成功）\n2. `memory/` 下是否出现新的 `*-session-summary.md`（→ session-summary hook 成功）\n\n如果两点都有 → 全链路修复成功。\n\n---\n\n步骤4（wiki-learn 401）在等待期间可以做，但那是另一个独立任务。你要现在诊断修复，还是等下次 /new 验证确认链路通顺后再一起处理？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":540,"cacheRead":89920,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90460,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0.0006479999999999999,"cacheRead":0.005395199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0060431999999999994}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776429765047,"responseId":"06315dc5767576bf76293cb17a7132fd"}}
