{"type":"message","id":"755d1a75","parentId":"33bdcd92","timestamp":"2026-04-17T12:52:52.789Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a comprehensive picture. Let me compile the full comparison.\n\nKey findings vs v2026.4.14:\n\n**Core Components:**\n| Component | Document | Actual | Status |\n|-----------|----------|--------|--------|\n| Gateway | 3100 | 18789 | ⚠️ 配置差异（文档说3100，实际18789）|\n| v8 Router (3102) | Gateway进程内 | 不存在 | ❌ |\n| v8 Scorer (3103) | 3103 | 3103 | ✅ |\n| v8 Classifier (3105) | 3105 | 3105 | ✅ |\n\n\n| Control UI | 18789 | 18789 | ✅ |\n\n**Advanced Features:**\n| Feature | Document | Actual | Status |\n|---------|----------|--------|--------|\n| Active Memory | 插件，可启用 | 已安装但DISABLED | ❌ |\n| Context Engine | 可插拔 | 未安装 | ❌ |\n| Lobster Workflow | DSL runtime | 已安装但DISABLED | ❌ |\n| Task Flow | Managed/Mirrored | 115个mirrored任务 | ⚠️ |\n\n虽然有115个mirrored任务，但这些都是外部观察对象，缺乏真正的Managed Task Flow，也没有实现Lobster这样的DSL runtime。\n\nBrowser插件已加载但没有Edge CDP配置，羊毛系统等其他组件还需要继续检查。","thinkingSignature":"b32eaf5ef3e531b3856306ebd2f77e73c8e722297660c44c5535b741b02a1911"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5egm2x2gf8wz_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Check skills directory and ClawHub\necho \"=== workspace skills ===\"\nls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/ 2>/dev/null | head -20\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== clawhub skill count ===\"\nwc -l ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/entities/*.md 2>/dev/null | tail -1\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Three-layer memory check ===\"\nls ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/ephemeral/ 2>/dev/null | tail -3\nls ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/*session-summary*.md 2>/dev/null | tail -3\necho \"MEMORY.md exists: $([ -f ~/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md ] && echo YES || echo NO)\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":49692,"output":457,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71787,"cost":{"input":0.0149076,"output":0.0005484,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"ca