{"type":"message","id":"9c253f75","parentId":"959a0c82","timestamp":"2026-04-17T13:02:28.692Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_8og9nhghxg0r_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"│              │          │          │          │ memory into prompt context.                              │           │\n│ @openclaw/   │ volcengi │ openclaw │ loaded   │ stock:volcengine/index.js                                │ 2026.4.15 │\n│ volcengine-  │ ne       │          │          │ OpenClaw Volcengine provider plugin                      │           │\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"fast-crest","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"│              │          │          │          │ memory into prompt context.                              │           │\n│ @openclaw/   │ volcengi │ openclaw │ loaded   │ stock:volcengine/index.js                                │ 2026.4.15 │\n│ volcengine-  │ ne       │          │          │ OpenClaw Volcengine provider plugin                      │           │\n","name":"node ~/.nvm/versions/node/v.../openclaw/openclaw.mjs"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776430948621}}
{"type":"message","id":"f935589b","parentId":"9c253f75","timestamp":"2026-04-17T13:02:34.263Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No \"context engine\" or \"lossless-claw\" plugin found. The document's Context Engine might be referring to a conceptual component (the context management system already built into the gateway) rather than a plugin that needs to be installed.\n\nLet me re-read the document's section on Context Engine to understand what it actually means.","thinkingSignature":"a380c127dbf7783ce46de245fa971841c1e89306d34ff722f158840dc421ed65"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9yp4zkuo33d6_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Search for context engine in the doc\ngrep -A 20 \"Context Engine\" /mnt/c/Users/ll/Desktop/.openclaw/workspace/main/OpenClaw-v2026.4.14-完整功能框架.md 2>/dev/null | head -40"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":44792,"output":148,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66578,"cost":{"input":0.0134376,"output":0.00017759999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01491348}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776430948694,"responseId":"06316264b795ce37f28edb5c5f03a76a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2ae00067","parentId":"f935589b","timestamp":"2026-04-17T13:02:34.800Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_9yp4zkuo33d6_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"32. [Context Engine 上下文引擎](#32-context-engine-上下文引擎)\n33. [Delegate Architecture 委托架构](#33-delegate-architecture-委托架构)\n34. [Usage Tracking 用量追踪](#34-usage-tracking-用量追踪)\n35. [Retry Policy 重试策略](#35-retry-policy-重试策略)\n36. [SOUL.md 人格撰写指南](#36-soulmd-人格撰写指南)\n\n---\n\n## 1. 核心定位\n\n**OpenClaw = 本地 AI Gateway + 多渠道消息中枢 + 推理引擎编排器**\n\n| 维度 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **本质** | 部署在自己硬件上的自托管服务，数据完全自主 |\n| **核心价值** | 一个进程同时对接所有聊天渠道，统一连接到 AI 推理引擎 |\n| **差异化** | Agent 原生（工具/记忆/多Agent路由）、自托管、多渠道 |\n| **License** | MIT，开源，社区驱动 |\n\n**设计哲学：**\n- 隐私优先：所有数据留在本地\n--\n## 32. Context Engine 上下文引擎\n\n### 32.1 定位\n\n**Context Engine** 是 OpenClaw v2026.4.x 引入的可插拔上下文组件，控制每次模型运行时如何构建 context：包含哪些 messages、如何摘要历史、如何管理 subagent 边界的上下文。\n\n内置 legacy 引擎，可通过插件替换为更高级的上下文管理方案。\n\n### 32.2 生命周期节点\n\n每次模型 prompt，Context Engine 在四个节点参与：\n\n| 节点 | 时机 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **Ingest** | 新消息加入 session 时 | 引擎可存储/索引消息 |\n| **Assemble** | 每次模型运行前 | 返回适配 token budget 的有序 messages 列表 |\n| **Compact** | context 满或 `/compact` 时 | 摘要旧历史释放空间 |\n| **After turn** | 运行完成后 | 持久化状态/触发后台压缩/更新索引 |"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":233,"aggregated":"32. [Context Engine 上下文引擎](#32-context-engine-上下文引擎)\n33. [Delegate Architecture 委托架构](#33-delegate-architecture-委托架构)\n34. [Usage Tracking 用量追踪](#34-usage-tracking-用量追踪)\n35. [Retry Policy 重试策略](#35-retry-policy-重试策略)\n36. [SOUL.md 人格撰写指南](#36-soulmd-人格撰写指南)\n\n---\n\n## 1. 核心定位\n\n**OpenClaw = 本地 AI Gateway + 多渠道消息中枢 + 推理引擎编排器**\n\n| 维度 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **本质** | 部署在自己硬件上的自托管服务，数据完全自主 |\n| **核心价值** | 一个进程同时对接所有聊天渠道，统一连接到 AI 推理引擎 |\n| **差异化** | Agent 原生（工具/记忆/多Agent路由）、自托管、多渠道 |\n| **License** | MIT，开源，社区驱动 |\n\n**设计哲学：**\n- 隐私优先：所有数据留在本地\n--\n## 32. Context Engine 上下文引擎\n\n### 32.1 定位\n\n**Context Engine** 是 OpenClaw v2026.4.x 引入的可插拔上下文组件，控制每次模型运行时如何构建 context：包含哪些 messages、如何摘要历史、如何管理 subagent 边界的上下文。\n\n内置 legacy 引擎，可通过插件替换为更高级的上下文管理方案。\n\n### 32.2 生命周期节点\n\n每次模型 prompt，Context Engine 在四个节点参与：\n\n| 节点 | 时机 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **Ingest** | 新消息加入 session 时 | 引擎可存储/索引消息 |\n| **Assemble** | 每次模型运行前 | 返回适配 token budget 的有序 messages 列表 |\n| **Compact** | context 满或 `/compact` 时 | 摘要旧历史释放空间 |\n| **After turn** | 运行完成后 | 持久化状态/触发后台压缩/更新索引 |","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776430954731}}
{"type":"message","id":"f0d8f2be","parentId":"2ae00067","timestamp":"2026-04-17T13:02:47.076Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Context Engine is a **pluggable architecture** - the built-in \"legacy engine\" is already running. The plugin system allows replacing it with a more advanced context management solution. There's no separate \"Context Engine plugin\" that needs to be installed - the functionality is built into the gateway itself.\n\nSo Context Engine = ✅ already in gateway (built-in legacy engine), and it's working as part of the bootstrap system.\n\nNow let me focus on Browser automation. The document says:\n1. Windows Edge with remote-debugging-port=9222\n2. netsh portproxy 9222→19222\n3. WSL Playwright CDP connects to localhost:19222\n\nThe browser plugin is loaded but Edge isn't running. \n\nSince this is WSL, I need to verify whether Edge is actually reachable from this environment or if it's only available on the Windows side.","thinkingSignature":"04c1b2a7656b9c74963be9c9f28ea1ba3339ee0f85e78c7eaa4ba03da8d3d38d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pi8odias6n8k_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Test if Edge CDP is reachable from Windows side\ncurl -s --connect-timeout 3 http://localhost:9222/json 2>/dev/null | head -3 || echo \"Edge CDP not reachable on Windows localhost:9222\"\n\necho \"\"\n# Check if there's a portproxy set up\nnetsh interface portproxy show all 2>/dev/null | head -15 || echo \"netsh not available (not on Windows or no admin)\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":45370,"output":292,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67300,"cost":{"input":0.013611,"output":0.0003504,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.015259680000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776430954802,"responseId":"0631626a456845d5c83220f3373e17fe"}}
