{"type":"message","id":"d9d53c7e","parentId":"ed8f571c","timestamp":"2026-04-17T14:02:20.314Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user says \"审查\" (audit/review). Given the context of our long session about auditing and fixing the OpenClaw framework, they likely want me to do another audit of the system state. Let me do a quick but thorough check of the current system state.","thinkingSignature":"f2071f8bd9ba59fc65cd880b9650d04b6426b8eeacc9840a23abd6b571758d18"},{"type":"text","text":"<thinking>\n### 1. 需求拆解\n用户要求\"审查\"——需要全面检查当前系统实际运行状态，不是之前那种对比文档，而是真实的实时状态核查。\n\n### 2. 方案推演\n按模块快速核查：\n1. 核心服务状态（端口 + 进程）\n2. 插件加载状态\n3. Cron jobs 最近状态\n4. 记忆链路（ephemeral 最近写入）\n5. Chromium CDP 持久化\n6. Gateway 日志有无报错\n\n### 3. 自我质疑\n这是被动等待后的主动审查，用户可能担心系统状态。不需要多步操作，只需要读取状态然后给出报告。\n\n### 4. 最终决策\n执行多路并发检查命令，汇总结果输出。\n</thinking>\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9c0htcowk0g0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 核心服务 ===\"\nss -tlnp 2>/dev/null | grep -E '3103|3105|18789|9222|3106'\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Gateway ===\"\nsystemctl --user status openclaw-gateway.service 2>/dev/null | grep -E \"Active|Main PID|Memory\" | head -3\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Chromium ===\"\nsystemctl --user status chromium-cdp.service 2>/dev/null | grep -E \"Active|Main PID\" | head-2\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 插件 ===\"\nnode ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/openclaw.mjs plugins list 2>&1 | grep -E \"active.memory|lobster|browser\" | grep -v grep"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58,"output":407,"cacheRead":77588,"cacheWrite":231,"totalTokens":78284,"cost":{"input":0.0000174,"output":0.0004883999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0046552799999999995,"cacheWrite":0.000086625,"total":0.005247704999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776434526507,"responseId":"0631705e38190af87fbf9aea9359e40a"}}
