{"type":"message","id":"b827f38b","parentId":"a859f8ab","timestamp":"2026-04-17T14:21:10.544Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found several issues:1. **Listener**: `intent` and `score` both point to the same URL `http://localhost:3103/api/score`. The intent endpoint should be different (the old v1 format or a proper intent endpoint). The v8 scorer only has `/api/score`, not `/api/intent`.2. **Active Memory**: Only has `enabled: true` with no other config. Default settings might be too aggressive (runs on every message).3. **auth-profiles**: minimax key is present ✅4. **v8 Scorer issue**: Returned all-zeros score - might be because the text was too simple. Let me test with a more complex task.Let me now check:1. The browser CDP2. Gateway logs for errors3. The 3100 port service","thinkingSignature":"f1cf8c17f89c2ee0ea9c25476acc0c6e22b3bc3b70575afda4f24ada4b169f07"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pt9krq7u3bqs_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 6. Browser CDP 实际测试 ===\"\nagent-browser --cdp 9222 url 2>&1\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 7. Gateway 日志 WARN/ERROR ===\"\njournalctl --user -u openclaw-gateway.service -n 100 2>/dev/null | grep -iE \"WARN|ERROR|Error|FATAL\" | tail -10 || echo \"无\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 8. Listener 日志 ===\"\ntail -20 /tmp/openclaw-listener.log 2>/dev/null | grep -iE \"error|warn|connect\" || echo \"无错误日志\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":61832,"output":328,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83798,"cost":{"input":0.0185496,"output":0.00039359999999999997,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02024148}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776435660911,"responseId":"063174cbd7f714e24b170c8a31f8ae34"}}
