{"type":"message","id":"2c6a1ef5","parentId":"d492b22b","timestamp":"2026-04-17T16:11:45.226Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants a deep comparison between the actual running system and the v2026.4.14 documentation. This is a comprehensive task that requires examining multiple aspects of the system against the documented specifications. Let me think about what needs to be checked.\n\nThe document covers 36 sections. I need to go through each major section and compare what's documented vs what's actually running.\n\nKey areas to verify:\n1. Core ports (3100, 3102, 3103, 3105, 18789) - vs actual\n2. Gateway components\n3. Agent loop lifecycle\n4. Bootstrap system\n5. Prompt assembly\n6. Three-layer memory\n7. v8 routing system\n\n\n8. Tool system\n9. Skills system\n10. Automation (Cron + Hooks)\n11. Session management\n12. Message queue\n13. Media support\n14. Channel system\n15. Node system\n16. Web UI & remote access\n17. Security\n18. Model system\n19. Streaming & Chunking\n20. Sandbox isolation\n21. Multi-agent routing\n22. Plugin system\n23. ACP protocol\n24. Lobster workflow\n25. Task Flow\n26. Compaction\n27. Config system\n28. CLI commands\n29. Current running status\n30. Active Memory\n\nNow I need to continue with the remaining sections and then systematically compare each component against the actual system state to identify any gaps or misconfigurations.","thinkingSignature":"f509ce548ac561de77a3ee2f8b1249277b14b17f61c50a86d03a153530d85ea6"},{"type":"text","text":"<thinking>\n### 1. 需求拆解\n需要逐章节深入对比当前运行系统与 v2026.4.14 文档，找出所有差异，不停留在表面。\n\n### 2. 方案推演\n按文档章节逐项核查：\n1. **核心端口映射** - 文档 vs 实际\n2. **Gateway 架构** - 各组件是否齐全\n3. **Bootstrap 系统** - 各文件是否齐全\n4. **Prompt 组装** - 各区块是否实际注入\n5. **三层记忆** - 每层是否真实可用\n6. **v8 路由** - 3102/3103/3105 实际状态\n7. **工具系统** - 各工具是否实现\n8. **Skills** - 加载机制\n9. **Cron + Hooks** - 实际触发情况\n10. **模型系统** - provider 配置\n11. **Active Memory** - 是否真正工作\n12. **Lobster** - 是否真正工作\n13. **Browser