keys: \"threshold\", \"minTurnsBetween\"\n- <root>: Unrecognized key: \"context\"\n\n🦞 OpenClaw 2026.4.15 (041266a) — Automation with claws: minimal fuss, maximal pinch.\n\nUsage: openclaw sessions [options] [command]\n\nList stored conversation sessions\n\n","name":"node ~/.nvm/versions/node/v.../openclaw/openclaw.mjs"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776442824723}}
{"type":"message","id":"ff7d19d3","parentId":"c0086039","timestamp":"2026-04-17T16:20:35.670Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There are config validation errors:1. `agents.defaults.compaction.mode`: allowed values are \"default\" or \"safeguard\" - but I set it to \"safe\"\n2. `agents.defaults.compaction`: unrecognized keys \"threshold\", \"minTurnsBetween\"\n3. `<root>: context` - \"context\" is not a recognized top-level key\n\nSo the gateway config schema does NOT support a `context` top-level key. And the compaction settings have limited options.\n\nLet me fix the config - remove the invalid parts, and instead figure out what the gateway actually supports.\n\nThe valid compaction mode is \"safeguard\". The other options I tried are not valid.\n\nAnd the `context` top-level key doesn't exist in the schema. So I can't configure context management through openclaw.json.\n\n\nI need to restore the original config and start over. The gateway has a compaction mechanism with limited configuration, but there's no built-in way to manage context limits through openclaw.json. The real solution might involve writing a gateway hook or plugin instead. Let me check if there's a session-level compaction API or command I'm missing.","thinkingSignature":"f543c56d5b7a80f162d3d29a5456f96c57cb596b9c4d2eaadc1a29dca6905765"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_92rtc05a2gt9_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 恢复 gateway config - 移除无效字段\npython3 << 'EOF'\nimport json\n\nwith open('/home/ai/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'r') as f:\n    config = json.load(f)\n\n# 移除无效的 context 顶级配置\nif 'context' in config:\n    del config['context']\n\n# 修复 compaction\nif 'agents' in config and isinstance(config.get('agents'), dict):\n    agents_defaults = config['agents'].get('defaults', {})\n    if 'compaction' in agents_defaults:\n        # 只保留有效字段\n        compaction = agents_defaults['compaction']\n        if isinstance(compaction, dict):\n            compaction_mode = compaction.get('mode', 'safeguard')\n            if compaction_mode not in ('default', 'safeguard'):\n                compaction_mode = 'safeguard'\n            agents_defaults['compaction'] = {'mode': compaction_mode}\n\nwith open('/home/ai/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(config, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\n\nprint(\"config fixed\")\nEOF"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":101708,"output":482,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":123828,"cost":{"input":0.0305124,"output":0.0005784,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03238908}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776442824791,"responseId":"063190c50c04aae3e854ff623ed8a624"}}
