{"type":"message","id":"81ae6445","parentId":"a166fed4","timestamp":"2026-04-17T16:22:44.988Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gateway is running. Let me give a quick summary.","thinkingSignature":"ce0776994a37757d3c2ce161b717233e4df6c8ed6f568bdcc3b39917d2b64511"},{"type":"text","text":"Gateway 运行正常。\n\n## 已完成的上下文管理配置\n\n**1. context-monitor cron**（每30分钟检查）\n- 直接读取 session context 文件\n- token 超过 120K 触发压缩\n- 保留最近 15 轮 + 摘要\n\n**2. compaction 模式**：`safeguard`（已验证可用）\n\n**3. 上下文阈值**：\n- MiniMax-M2.7 contextWindow: 204800\n- 摘要触发线: 120000（75%）\n- 截断线: 160000\n\n**4. 当前 session**：0 消息，无需压缩\n\n---\n\n配置已生效。下次 session 消息累积到阈值会自动压缩，不需要手动触发。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":100895,"output":162,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122695,"cost":{"input":0.0302685,"output":0.00019439999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03176118}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776442957370,"responseId":"0631914ca06e5e9244edb27eb80bc68e"}}
