{"type":"message","id":"35168ba9","parentId":"0b56434b","timestamp":"2026-04-17T16:23:48.693Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking whether after scoring, I actually follow the recommended strategy (DIRECT/STEP/SUBAGENT/PARALLEL/MEGA) when executing tasks. This is a great question about the actual execution behavior.\n\nLet me think about this:\n\n1. The v8 scorer returns a `recommendedStrategy` field\n2. But does the gateway actually USE this field to route execution?\n3. Or do I (the agent) just receive the score as context and decide myself?\n\nFrom what I know about OpenClaw's architecture:\n- The `recommendedStrategy` is written to ephemeral storage as part of the scoring\n- But the actual routing decision might be up to the agent (me) to interpret and act on\n\n\n- The AGENTS.md says to use the orchestrator for multi-step tasks, but I'm not sure if that's actually happening in practice or if I'm just handling it myself based on the score I see.\n\nSo the honest answer is: I don't know for certain without checking the gateway code, and even if the recommendedStrategy is generated, there's no guarantee the system actually routes tasks accordingly—it might just be informational context for me to decide on.","thinkingSignature":"e1cf0ecd045312e58ef5fca43bfcd3fe1f99138f0f8079f0d2f682e783fa4e9b"},{"type":"text","text":"<thinking>\n### 1. 需求拆解\n用户问的是：评分给出的策略推荐（DIRECT/SUBAGENT/PARALLEL/MEGA），在实际任务执行时是否被真正使用。\n\n### 2. 方案推演\n这需要查看实际执行路径。评分结果写入 ephemeral，但实际 spawn subagent 是什么时候触发的？是 gateway 根据策略自动执行，还是 agent（我）看到分数后自己决定？\n\n### 3. 自我质疑\n我需要诚实回答：我只知道评分链路通了，但评分结果是否真的驱动了执行路径，我不确定。\n\n### 4. 最终决策\n诚实地回答：我收到了评分上下文，但不确定系统是否根据策略自动执行。给出一个测试方法让用户自己验证。\n</thinking>\n\n说实话：**我不确定。**\n\n评分结果写入了 ephemeral，我能看到 `recommendedStrategy: SPAWN_SUBAGENT` 这个上下文。但这只是给我参考，还是 gateway 会自动按策略执行，我无法确认。\n\n**验证方法**——发一个需要 subagent 的任务，看实际行为：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l8s73lba28fy_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3103/api/score \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"text\":\"分析 ~/projects 目录下所有代码文件，审查每个文件的逻辑错误并生成完整报告\"}' | python3 -m json.tool"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":528,"cacheRead":122734,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":123262,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0.0006336,"cacheRead":0.00736404,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00799764}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776443012227,"responseId":"063191839b26dad68055a3f0d0320f0e"}}
