{"type":"message","id":"792916d2","parentId":"58a570b0","timestamp":"2026-04-17T16:45:36.992Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-04-18 00:45 GMT+8] 学习，思考后给我答复，不要操作：\n\n---\n\n## 完整方案：Hook 派发 + 子Agent 自返程\n\n### 架构流程\n\n```\n用户消息 → Hook (message:preprocessed)\n │\n ├─ 调用分类器 (3104)\n ├─ 确定目标 Agent (executor / planner)\n ├─ 获取当前 session 的 parent key (用于返程)\n ├─ 构造派发指令，注入到 bodyForAgent\n │\n ▼\n 主 Agent 收到指令 → 调用 sessions_spawn\n │\n ├─ 派发子 Agent，传入：\n │ - 原始任务\n │ - parent session key (作为 metadata)\n │\n ▼\n 子 Agent 启动 → 读取 parent session key → 执行任务\n │\n └─ 完成后，调用 sessions_send 将结果发回 parent session\n │\n ▼\n 主 session 收到结果 → Gateway 推送到渠道 → 用户看到\n```\n\n### 关键设计\n\n1. **Hook 不派发，只注入指令**：Hook 无法直接调用 `sessions_spawn`，但可以修改 `bodyForAgent`，让主 Agent 去执行派发。\n2. **传递返程地址**：Hook 将当前 session 的唯一标识（`parentSessionKey`）写入指令中，主 Agent 在派发时将其作为 `metadata` 传给子 Agent。\n3. **子 Agent 自返程**：子 Agent 的 `SOUL.md` 中约定：启动时检查 `metadata.parentSessionKey`，若存在，则在任务完成后主动调用 `sessions_send` 将结果发回。\n\n---\n\n## 一、Hook 代码（`message:preprocessed`）\n\n**文件**：`~/.openclaw/extensions/auto-router/index.js`\n\n```javascript\nconst axios = require('axios');\n\nconst CLASSIFIER_URL = process.env.CLASSIFIER_URL || 'http://localhost:3104/classify';\n\nconst SCENE_TO_AGENT = {\n code_generation: 'executor',\n task_multi_step: 'executor',\n high_risk_automated: 'executor',\n math_reasoning: 'planner',\n expert_user: 'planner',\n fault_recovery: 'planner',\n};\nconst DEFAULT_AGENT = 'executor';\n\n/**\n * 调用分类器获取场景\n */\nasync function classify(message) {\n try {\n const res = await axios.post(CLASSIFIER_URL, { text: message }, { timeout: 500 });\n return res.data.label || 'vague_request';\n } catch (e) {\n return null;\n }\n}\n\n/**\n * 判断是否为任务型场景\n */\nfunction isTaskScene(scene) {\n const taskScenes = ['code_generation', 'task_multi_step', 'high_risk_automated',\n 'math_reasoning', 'expert_user', 'fault_recovery'];\n return taskScenes.includes(scene);\n}\n\n/**\n * 主 Hook 函数\n */\nexports.messagePreprocessed = async function(event) {\n const userMessage = event.context?.bodyForAgent;\n const parentSessionKey = event.context?.sessionKey; // 获取当前 session 的唯一标识\n\n if (!userMessage) return;\n\n // 1. 调用分类器\n const scene = await classify(userMessage);\n if (!scene || !isTaskScene(scene)) {\n return; // 非任务，让主 Agent 正常处理\n }\n\n // 2. 确定目标 Agent\n const targetAgent = SCENE_TO_AGENT[scene] || DEFAULT_AGENT;\n\n // 3. 构造派发指令，注入到 bodyForAgent\n const spawnInstruction = `\n[系统指令 - 最高优先级]\n请立即使用 sessions_spawn 工具派发一个子 Agent 来处理以下任务。\n\n参数：\n- agentId: ${targetAgent}\n- message: \"${userMessage.replace(/\"/g, '\\\\\"')}\"\n- metadata: { \"parentSessionKey\": \"${parentSessionKey}\", \"originalTask\": \"${userMessage.replace(/\"/g, '\\\\\"')}\" }\n\n派发完成后，你的本轮回复仅输出：\n\"[系统] 任务已派发给子 Agent (${targetAgent})，请等待执行结果。\"\n不得输出任何其他内容。\n\n[原始用户消息]\n${userMessage}\n`;\n\n event.context.bodyForAgent = spawnInstruction;\n console.log(`[auto-router] Injected spawn instruction for agent: ${targetAgent}`);\n};\n```\n\n---\n\n## 二、子 Agent 返程逻辑（SOUL.md 补充）\n\n为 `executor` 和 `planner` 两个 Agent 的 `SOUL.md` 添加以下规则（放在文件最开头）：\n\n**文件**：`~/.openclaw/agents/executor/SOUL.md` 和 `~/.openclaw/agents/planner/SOUL.md`\n\n```markdown\n## [!!] 返程发送（最高优先级）\n\n**在处理任何用户请求之前，你必须先检查当前会话的 metadata。**\n\n1. 读取当前会话的 metadata（通过系统注入的上下文）。\n2. 检查 `metadata.parentSessionKey` 是否存在。\n3. **若存在**：\n - 这意味着你是一个被派发的子 Agent。\n - 正常处理用户请求，生成完整的回复。\n - 在回复生成完毕后，**立即**调用工具 `sessions_send`，参数如下：\n - `sessionKey`: `metadata.parentSessionKey` 的值\n - `message`: 你刚刚生成的完整回复内容\n - 调用完成后，你的本轮回复可以正常结束（或输出简短确认，但 `sessions_send` 已经将结果发回，主 session 的用户已经看到）。\n4. **若不存在**：正常处理请求，无需额外操作。\n\n> 此规则确保子 Agent 的结果能够返回到调用方 session，实现端到端的自动化派发闭环。\n```\n\n---\n\n## 三、部署步骤\n\n### 1. 创建 Hook 目录并写入代码\n```bash\nmkdir -p ~/.openclaw/extensions/auto-router\n# 将上述 Hook 代码复制到 ~/.openclaw/extensions/auto-router/index.js\n```\n\n### 2. 注册 Hook\n编辑 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`，在 `plugins.entries` 中添加：\n```json\n{\n \"plugins\": {\n \"entries\": {\n \"auto-router\": {\n \"enabled\": true,\n \"path\": \"/home/ai/.openclaw/extensions/auto-router/index.js\"\n }\n }\n }\n}\n```\n\n### 3. 更新子 Agent 的 SOUL.md\n```bash\n# 编辑 executor 的 SOUL.md\nnano ~/.openclaw/agents/executor/SOUL.md\n# 将上述返程规则粘贴到文件最开头\n\n# 编辑 planner 的 SOUL.md\nnano ~/.openclaw/agents/planner/SOUL.md\n# 同样粘贴返程规则\n```\n\n### 4. 确保子 Agent 存在\n```bash\n# 如果尚未创建，请先创建\nopenclaw agents add executor\nopenclaw agents add planner\n```\n\n### 5. 重启 Gateway\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n---\n\n## 四、验证\n\n发送一条任务型消息（如“帮我写一个 Python 快排”）。预期行为：\n\n1. 主 Agent 输出：`[系统] 任务已派发给子 Agent (executor)，请等待执行结果。`\n2. 片刻后，用户在同一对话中收到子 Agent 返回的代码结果。\n\n查看日志确认流程：\n```bash\ntail -f /tmp/openclaw/openclaw-*.log | grep -E \"auto-router|sessions_spawn|sessions_send\"\n```\n\n---"}],"timestamp":1776444336932}}
{"type":"message","id":"e48e6639","parentId":"792916d2","timestamp":"2026-04-17T16:46:12.784Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a very thorough and well-designed scheme. Let me analyze it critically before giving my assessment.\n\n**The architecture flow:**\n1. User message → Hook (message:preprocessed)\n2. Hook modifies bodyForAgent → injects spawn instruction\n3. Main Agent reads modified message → calls sessions_spawn\n4. Subagent receives task + parentSessionKey metadata\n5. Subagent does work → calls sessions_send back to parent\n6. Parent session receives result → user sees it\n\n**Critical analysis:**\n\n**What this scheme gets right:**\n- It leverages the Agent's existing capability (sessions_spawn) rather than trying to bypass it\n\n\n- Parent session key gets passed through metadata to enable the return path\n- The subagent consults its SOUL.md on startup to check for parentSessionKey and handle the callback automatically\n- Even though the main agent still outputs one message, the subagent's result reaches the user directly\n\n**Problems with the scheme:**\n\nThe `messagePreprocessed` export naming convention doesn't align with how existing hooks actually register—they use `handler` as the default export. While the function could theoretically be invoked by name, I need to verify whether the gateway actually calls exported functions by name or expects a specific entry point.\n\nMore critically, modifying `bodyForAgent` to inject a natural language instruction won't reliably trigger a `sessions_spawn` tool call—the agent might just acknowledge the instruction verbally without spawning anything. For guaranteed execution, the instruction would need to be in tool-call JSON format, but that's essentially what the agent already does, so this approach doesn't actually solve the core problem.\n\nThe metadata.parentSessionKey concept is sound in theory, but there's no guarantee the agent will pass it through to the subagent's session context when spawning. The subagent also can't directly read metadata from the spawning session—the parameter just gets forwarded, not actually injected into the subagent's own context. This is a fundamental limitation of the sessions_spawn tool that the scheme doesn't address.\n\nMore importantly, the scheme assumes separate executor and planner agents exist, but I haven't verified they actually do.\n\nLooking at the agent directories, I only see coder, codex, deep, deep_agent, fast, fast_agent, main, and thinker. The specific agents the scheme targets (executor and planner) don't exist, and the user only has a single main agent configured.\n\nBut even if these agents were created, there's a fundamental issue with the injection approach. The modified message wouldn't trigger a sessions_spawn tool call unless the agent is specifically designed to recognize and execute that pattern. The whole scheme hinges on this working, but it's unclear whether it actually would.\n\nThe core problem remains: there's no reliable way to get the agent to spawn a subagent from within the auto-score-classify hook. The user keeps designing schemes that assume the agent will see modified context and act on it, but the agent doesn't have a built-in mechanism to do that consistently.","thinkingSignature":"4adf5b6ce3db88c1813f0dc0f26243cc00be911f141355624cbf471a9df449a8"},{"type":"text","text":"## 评估\n\n这个方案比之前所有版本都更完整。核心突破：**不依赖 Gateway 支持，通过修改消息内容 + 跨 session 通信实现闭环**。\n\n---\n\n### 真正可行的部分\n\n**返程机制**（sessions_send 回到 parent session）——这是真实有效的设计。gateway 支持 sessions_send，subagent 结果能回到主 session。\n\n---\n\n### 仍存在的问题\n\n**1. 子 Agent 不存在**\n\n```\nagents/ 目录：coder, codex, deep, deep_agent, fast, fast_agent, main, thinker\n```\n\n`executor` 和 `planner` 需要先创建，否则 sessions_spawn 失败。\n\n**2. bodyForAgent 注入不触发工具调用**\n\n你注入的是自然语言指令，不是工具调用 JSON。Agent 看到指令可能只是回复\"好的，我派发了\"，而不是真的调用 sessions_spawn。\n\n需要注入的是：\n```json\n{\"tool\": \"sessions_spawn\", \"params\": {...}}\n```\n但这样 Agent 也不一定解析——它是处理文本的，不是处理结构化 JSON 的。\n\n**3. metadata.parentSessionKey subagent 读不到**\n\n`sessions_spawn` 传入的参数和 subagent 的 SOUL.md 加载是两回事。subagent 启动时只能从消息内容里解析 parentSessionKey，不能从\"metadata\"字段读取。\n\n---\n\n### 最关键的问题\n\n这个方案的核心依赖是：**Agent 会按照 Hook 注入的指令去调用 sessions_spawn**。\n\n但 Agent 不是执行代码，是生成文本。它看到指令可能：\n- 调用 sessions_spawn（你希望的）\n- 输出\"任务已派发\"然后结束（最可能）\n\n这不是配置问题，是 Agent 的本质行为——**它不会把文本指令变成工具调用，除非指令本身是工具调用格式且上下文足够清晰**。\n\n---\n\n### 结论\n\n方案设计思路对，返程机制可行，但依赖 Agent 主动派发这个前提本身不可靠。需要测试验证：发一条测试消息，Agent 是否真的会调用 sessions_spawn。如果不会，则整个方案失效。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58,"output":1014,"cacheRead":136466,"cacheWrite":2100,"totalTokens":139638,"cost":{"input":0.0000174,"output":0.0012167999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00818796,"cacheWrite":0.0007875,"total":0.010209659999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776444337050,"responseId":"063196b135b49ccc39f9d3909d35b143"}}
