{"type":"message","id":"83030a67","parentId":"a25a273e","timestamp":"2026-04-17T16:46:49.746Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is another meta-level instruction from the user. The user wants me to think deeply about this problem again. But at this point, I've already done deep analysis multiple times. Let me think deeply about whether there's any fundamentally new insight I can add.\n\nLet me think about what we've established:\n1. Hook runs before agent, can't stop agent\n2. Injecting into bodyForAgent - may or may not work, depends on if agent interprets as tool call\n3. sessions_send works for return path\n4. SOUL.md rules only load at session start, not per-message\n5. Agent doesn't natively convert text instructions to tool calls\n\nThe fundamental architecture issue: the agent loop is a request-response pattern. The \"auto-routing\" described in documentation assumes gateway-level automatic routing, but that's not implemented.\n\n\nThe real question is whether agent will actually invoke sessions_spawn when given the instruction in text form. Looking at how agents work, they call tools when the system prompt explicitly tells them to in tool-call format, and even then they prefer responding with text. The most honest path forward is either implementing the complete solution and testing it, modifying the gateway to support hook-based spawning directly, or sticking with manual routing. I should give a clear recommendation rather than continuing to theorize.","thinkingSignature":"bf92969eede17397d8bd8f31085f3913aec4c2fa9f92869535f5734afc65d66c"},{"type":"text","text":"\n## 终极分析\n\n经过多轮讨论，核心问题已经收敛到一个点：\n\n**Agent 是否会把文本指令变成 sessions_spawn 调用？**\n\n---\n\n### 三种可能\n\n| 行为 | 概率 | 结果 |\n|------|------|------|\n| Agent 真的调用 sessions_spawn | 低 | 返程成功，用户看到结果 |\n| Agent 输出\"任务已派发\"然后结束 | 高 | 用户只看到废话，subagent 白跑 |\n| Agent 完全忽略指令 | 低 | 主 agent 处理任务，用户看到正常结果 |\n\n---\n\n### 根本原因\n\nAgent 是**文本生成器**，不是**指令执行器**。它擅长：\n- 生成代码\n- 生成分析\n- 生成回复\n\n它不擅长：\n- 把一段\"请调用 sessions_spawn\"的描述变成实际的工具调用\n- 除非系统 prompt 里明确告诉它\"遇到 X 格式就调用 Y 工具\"\n\n---\n\n### 唯一诚实的下一步\n\n**实际测试**：发一条指令给 agent，看它是否调用 sessions_spawn。\n\n不是纸上推演，不是在 SKILL.md 里加规则，是**真的发一条消息，看 agent 行为**。\n\n然后根据结果决定：\n- 如果 agent 真的调用了 → 方案可行，继续实现\n- 如果 agent 没有调用 → 放弃这个方案，接受当前架构上限\n\n---\n\n### 我的立场\n\n方案设计已经足够完善。继续讨论而不测试是在浪费精力。**建议现在执行一次真实的测试**，而不是继续规划。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58,"output":563,"cacheRead":137444,"cacheWrite":1599,"totalTokens":139664,"cost":{"input":0.0000174,"output":0.0006755999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00824664,"cacheWrite":0.000599625,"total":0.009539264999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776444391600,"responseId":"063196e5a0967f4050ed8690c85970bc"}}
