{"type":"message","id":"03ea854a","parentId":"83c5df27","timestamp":"2026-04-17T16:56:40.385Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user sent a normal test message without [AUTO_ROUTE] - they want me to just respond to the quicksort request. This is actually the quicksort code itself being tested, not the AUTO_ROUTE mechanism. Let me just write the quicksort code.","thinkingSignature":"f71e3c460b0aa70ab592b2525049e1e87e7b050bc70d51589992a1918f78148f"},{"type":"text","text":"```python\ndef quick_sort(arr):\n    if len(arr) <= 1:\n        return arr\n    pivot = arr[len(arr) // 2]\n    left = [x for x in arr if x < pivot]\n    middle = [x for x in arr if x == pivot]\n    right = [x for x in arr if x > pivot]\n    return quick_sort(left) + middle + quick_sort(right)\n\n# 测试\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    nums = [3, 6, 8, 10, 1, 2, 1]\n    print(\"原数组:\", nums)\n    print(\"排序后:\", quick_sort(nums))\n```\n\n```\n原数组: [3, 6, 8, 10, 1, 2, 1]\n排序后: [1, 1, 2, 3, 6, 8, 10]\n```\n\n这是一条普通消息，所以正常回复了代码。\n\n---\n\n要测试 AUTO_ROUTE，需要你修改 SOUL.md 后 `/new` 再发带 `[AUTO_ROUTE]` 标记的消息。要继续测试吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":295,"cacheRead":141473,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":141768,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0.000354,"cacheRead":0.008488379999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.008842379999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776444989385,"responseId":"0631993b4e3ef5bbed849eda38dfecfa"}}
