{"type":"message","id":"ef690d1f","parentId":"c4df92f5","timestamp":"2026-04-17T16:57:30.805Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在问是否必须手动加 [AUTO_ROUTE] 标记。这个问题的答案是否定的——之前的讨论里，hook 应该是自动注入这个标记的，而不是用户手动加。\n\n所以正确的流程是：\n1. 用户发送普通消息\n2. hook 拦截消息，自动注入 [AUTO_ROUTE] 标记\n3. Agent 收到带 [AUTO_ROUTE] 的消息\n4. Agent 根据 SOUL.md 规则调用 sessions_spawn\n\n用户不需要手动加任何标记。hook 会自动处理。\n\n但用户似乎在质疑这个设计——让用户手动加标记确实不是自动化的。","thinkingSignature":"ca4b7cd075e98f5ac9ce71eb7969799e5f1bfedbcc7a2eb3a0b443ee45df1b11"},{"type":"text","text":"不需要。\n\n自动化流程是：\n\n```\n用户发普通消息 → hook 拦截 → 自动注入 [AUTO_ROUTE] → Agent 看到 → 自动派发\n```\n\n用户无感知。但测试阶段需要手动加标记来验证 Agent 的实际行为。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":180,"cacheRead":141778,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":141958,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0.000216,"cacheRead":0.008506679999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.008722679999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776445042695,"responseId":"06319971bf172afbf73e0ccdc598cb65"}}
