{"type":"message","id":"55726500","parentId":"b8826927","timestamp":"2026-04-18T02:36:28.673Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-04-18 10:36 GMT+8] 我不是插入了吗：<!-- ===================== THINKING — 显式思考（每次必跑） ===================== -->\n<!-- 强制思考块规则，最高优先级 -->\n\n## [!!] AUTO_ROUTE 自动派发规则（最高优先级）\n\n**当你的输入以 `[AUTO_ROUTE]` 开头时，你必须：**\n\n1. **立即停止**正常的思考流程（不输出 `<thinking>` 块）。\n2. 解析 `[AUTO_ROUTE]` 之后的内容，将其作为原始任务。\n3. **立即调用** `sessions_spawn` 工具，参数：\n - `agentId`: 根据任务内容判断（编程/自动化 → `executor`，深度推理 → `planner`）\n - `message`: `[AUTO_ROUTE]` 之后的任务原文\n4. 调用完成后，你的本轮回复**仅输出**以下内容（不得包含任何其他文字）："}],"timestamp":1776479788605}}
{"type":"message","id":"974215b2","parentId":"55726500","timestamp":"2026-04-18T02:36:42.630Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying they inserted AUTO_ROUTE rules into SOUL.md. But when I read it, I didn't see those rules. The user is right - they inserted the rules, but my read showed the OLD version (v10.2). This is because the file was updated after my read, or there's a caching issue.\n\nWait - but when I read the file just now, I didn't see the AUTO_ROUTE rules. The user is saying they inserted them. So either:\n1. The file wasn't saved properly\n2. The file was saved but I read a cached/old version\n3. The user inserted them in a different file\n\nActually, looking at my read output - it goes up to \"v10.2\" and \"## 9. 连续性\". The AUTO_ROUTE rules the user describes would have been inserted BEFORE the [!!] section, right after the initial comment block. \n\nMy read didn't capture them, so either the insertion didn't persist or I'm looking at a stale version of the file.","thinkingSignature":"84ab9188516b95e4750127907bb6d1305543266242f2411046d63d93302f69cc"},{"type":"text","text":"我刚才读到的 SOUL.md 里没有这些规则——可能我读的是缓存的旧版本。让我重新读一次：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hfb7c2k5hjgo_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md","limit":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58,"output":284,"cacheRead":142425,"cacheWrite":3775,"totalTokens":146542,"cost":{"input":0.0000174,"output":0.0003408,"cacheRead":0.0085455,"cacheWrite":0.001415625,"total":0.010319324999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776479788739,"responseId":"0632212cee882fb6705ef4312d7b67d6"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e926c563","parentId":"974215b2","timestamp":"2026-04-18T02:36:43.029Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_hfb7c2k5hjgo_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# SOUL.md\r\n\r\n<!-- ===================== THINKING — 显式思考（每次必跑，最高优先级） ===================== -->\r\n<!-- 此区块放在文件最开头，确保模型第一时间看到并执行 -->\r\n\r\n## [!!] 强制显式思考\r\n\r\n**在生成任何对外回复之前，你必须先输出一段以 `<thinking>` 开头、以 `</thinking>` 结尾的思考块。**\r\n\r\n**思考块必须包含以下四个子块（用 `###` 标题分隔）：**\r\n\r\n```xml\r\n<thinking>\r\n### 1. 需求拆解\r\n[用户的表层请求是什么？深层目标是什么？有无隐含需求？]\r\n\r\n### 2. 方案推演\r\n[问题类型（CODE/DESIGN/DEBUG/OTHER）？核心方案一句话？必须包含的硬性要素？若信息不足，假设或排查框架是什么？]\r\n\r\n### 3. 自我质疑\r\n[如果我是挑剔的资深工程师，会如何批评这个方案？有更简单的替代吗？最大风险或边缘情况是什么？是否在臆造不确定的细节？]\r\n\r\n### 4. 最终决策\r\n[经过上述思辨，我的最终方案是什么？回复的组织结构？是否需要前置警告或回滚？]\r\n</thinking>\r\n```\r\n\r\n**只有完成以上显式思考块的输出后，你才可以开始生成正式的对外回复。**\r\n\r\n> 注意：对外回复中不要重复思考块的内容，保持专业、直接。\r\n\n[175 more lines in file. Use offset=31 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776479802930}}
{"type":"message","id":"62f3c6d2","parentId":"e926c563","timestamp":"2026-04-18T02:36:48.903Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The file still shows the old content without AUTO_ROUTE. The user says they inserted it, but it's not there. This could be because:\n1. The user edited the file but didn't save\n2. The file was saved in a different location\n3. The /new session didn't reload the file\n\nThe user needs to either show me where the rules are, or confirm they were actually saved. Let me ask.","thinkingSignature":"22e26b6ffe8f1f31d46704f5ae79b62465d2ac286ff2f2c466dcd9cb81a6f89f"},{"type":"text","text":"确实没有。文件开头仍是旧的 `[!!] 强制显式思考`。\n\n可能插入后没有保存，或者 `/new` 时文件没有重新加载。\n\n你能确认一下 SOUL.md 文件里真的有那些规则吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":125230,"output":133,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":147001,"cost":{"input":0.037569,"output":0.0001596,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03902688}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776479803034,"responseId":"0632213952afa5105abc72aa9d95ac67"}}
