{"type":"message","id":"03908516","parentId":"013aac82","timestamp":"2026-04-18T02:48:24.633Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, sessions_spawn works without agentId. The tool call was successful and a subagent was spawned.\n\nNow according to the AUTO_ROUTE rule, after calling sessions_spawn, I should output NO_REPLY. Let me do that.\n\nActually wait - the subagent's task is just \"帮我写一个 Python 快排\". The subagent will receive this task, process it, and then... what? It needs to know to send the result back to the parent session. But it doesn't have a parentSessionKey.\n\nAlso, the subagent was spawned without a specific agentId, so which agent will process it? Maybe the default agent.\n\nLet me output NO_REPLY as the rule says, and wait for the subagent to complete.","thinkingSignature":"9b58bc13394a73b96baf6454c59e3ff3c5ffe3c351e1cafd5b1dba224f499cbc"},{"type":"text","text":"`sessions_spawn` 不接受 `agentId` 参数，只能用默认 agent。所以规则里的 `agentId` 判断逻辑在这个环境里**物理不可行**——工具不支持这个参数。\n\n**发现**：\n- `agentId` 参数 → `forbidden`\n- 不带 `agentId` → 可以派发，但目标 agent 不确定\n\n**结论**：SOUL.md 里的 AUTO_ROUTE 规则在这个环境里**无法完整执行**，因为 `sessions_spawn` 工具不接受 `agentId`。\n\nNO_REPLY"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":25684,"output":263,"cacheRead":18642,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44589,"cost":{"input":0.0077052,"output":0.0003156,"cacheRead":0.0011185199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00913932}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776480496891,"responseId":"063223f0d9e45b3e725d6914acd641fc"}}
