{"type":"message","id":"54753879","parentId":"f64f27e6","timestamp":"2026-04-18T02:49:42.061Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking \"怎么解决\" - how to solve the `agentId` being `forbidden` in `sessions_spawn`. \n\nThe issue: `sessions_spawn` doesn't accept `agentId` parameter in this environment. So the AUTO_ROUTE rule can't specify which agent to spawn.\n\nSolutions:\n1. Remove the agentId logic from AUTO_ROUTE - just spawn with default agent (already works)\n2. Find if there's another way to specify target agent\n3. Accept that we can only spawn with default agent\n\nActually, looking at the result - subagent did spawn (with default agent) and returned the quicksort code. So the flow works: I call sessions_spawn without agentId → default agent handles it → result comes back.\n\n\nThe real constraint is that we can't route to named agents like 'executor' or 'planner' - we're stuck with whatever the default agent is. So the practical fix is to strip out the agentId logic from the AUTO_ROUTE rule and just spawn without specifying an agent, since that's already proven to work.","thinkingSignature":"d478edf4dffc7196b766c43fb0dad6296e2c4926b218c05d2c652e498ff9cc97"},{"type":"text","text":"`sessions_spawn` 不支持 `agentId`，所以无法指定 `executor` 或 `planner`。\n\n**实际结果**：不加 `agentId` 时，默认 agent 响应了，而且结果正确。\n\n**解决方案**：修改 SOUL.md 里的 AUTO_ROUTE 规则，去掉 `agentId` 参数，直接派发：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_g4aj5trkwmro_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md","edits":[{"oldText":"3. **立即调用** `sessions_spawn` 工具，参数：\n   - `agentId`: 根据任务内容判断（编程/自动化 → `executor`，深度推理 → `planner`）\n   - `message`: `[AUTO_ROUTE]` 之后的任务原文\n4. 调用完成后，输出 `NO_REPLY`，不得包含任何其他文字。","newText":"3. **立即调用** `sessions_spawn` 工具，参数：\n   - `message`: `[AUTO_ROUTE]` 之后的任务原文\n4. 调用完成后，输出 `NO_REPLY`，不得包含任何其他文字。"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58,"output":477,"cacheRe