{"type":"message","id":"d5119cda","parentId":"833fd3e7","timestamp":"2026-04-18T02:53:17.138Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to use my initiative. Let me think about what I can do here.\n\nThe core problem: AUTO_ROUTE rules only work in the main session. The user wants automated dispatch but:\n1. AUTO_ROUTE in main session requires the user to manually send `[AUTO_ROUTE]` prefixed messages\n2. There's no way to automatically intercept all user messages and add the `[AUTO_ROUTE]` prefix\n\nBut wait - the auto-score-classify hook already runs on every message. What if the hook modifies the user's message to include `[AUTO_ROUTE]` prefix when the score is high?\n\nThe hook has access to `event.context.bodyForAgent`. It could:\n\n\n1. Check the score\n2. If score >= threshold, prepend `[AUTO_ROUTE]` to the message\n3. The main agent then sees `[AUTO_ROUTE]` and triggers the spawn rule\n\nBut there's a timing issue - the hook calls the scorer and writes results to ephemeral, but the main agent receives the modified message before it checks ephemeral for the score. So I'd need the hook to modify the message first, then the agent would see the prefix and know to spawn without needing to check ephemeral again.\n\nActually, this could work perfectly. When a user message comes in, the hook scores it, and if it's high enough, it rewrites `bodyForAgent` to prepend `[AUTO_ROUTE]`. The main agent receives that modified message, sees the prefix, and follows the AUTO_ROUTE rule to spawn a subagent, then outputs `NO_REPLY`. The subagent processes the task and returns the result directly to the user. I need to modify the auto-score-classify hook to implement this.","thinkingSignature":"3d2431efcc2e62cc1189d5ac1b3e432fa0747fea0212482a31bff7750d6954db"},{"type":"text","text":"hook 可以在评分后直接修改消息内容。我来改造 `auto-score-classify`，让高评分消息自动带上 `[AUTO_ROUTE]` 前缀：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9z9x69ayktn0_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/hooks/auto-score-classify/handler.js"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58,"output":422,"cacheRead":49759,"cacheWrite":771,"totalTokens":51010,"cost":{"input":0.0000174,"output":0.0005064,"cacheRead":0.0029855399999999996,"cacheWrite":0.000289125,"total":0.0037984649999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776480784879,"responseId":"063225107dbf2ee3120016d54ad8a9ad"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a0ee6055","parentId":"d5119cda","timestamp":"2026-04-18T02:53:17.538Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_9z9x69ayktn0_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// auto-score-classify hook v2\n// + 自动 fork 子 agent（score >= 40）\n// + 主 agent 标记文件（agent 检查后决定是否 NO_REPLY）\n\nimport fs from \"node:fs\";\nimport path from \"node:path\";\nimport http from \"node:http\";\nimport { spawn } from \"node:child_process\";\n\nconst GW_TOKEN = '5e7ab299281fb2ffbdbb922f9939d9abbe5e15321f6cb901';\nconst SCORE_THRESHOLD = 40;\nconst AUTO_SPAWN_THRESHOLD = 50;\n\nasync function fetchJSON(url, body, timeoutMs = 4000) {\n  return new Promise((resolve) => {\n    const postData = JSON.stringify(body);\n    const req = http.request(\n      url,\n      {\n        method: \"POST\",\n        headers: { \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\", \"Content-Length\": Buffer.byteLength(postData) },\n      },\n      (res) => {\n        let data = \"\";\n        res.on(\"data\", (chunk) => (data += chunk));\n        res.on(\"end\", () => {\n          try { resolve(JSON.parse(data)); }\n          catch { resolve(null); }\n        });\n      }\n    );\n    req.on(\"error\", () => resolve(null));\n    req.setTimeout(timeoutMs, () => { req.destroy(); resolve(null); });\n    req.write(postData);\n    req.end();\n    setTimeout(() => { try { req.destroy(); } catch {} }, timeoutMs);\n  });\n}\n\nasync function runClassification(text) {\n  return fetchJSON(\"http://127.0.0.1:3105/classify\", { text }, 4000);\n}\n\nasync function runScoring(prompt) {\n  return fetchJSON(\"http://127.0.0.1:3103/api/score\", { prompt }, 4000);\n}\n\nfunction ensureDir(dir) {\n  if (!fs.existsSync(dir)) {\n    fs.mkdirSync(dir, { recursive: true });\n  }\n}\n\n// ─── Meaningfulness filter ───────────────────────────────────────────────────\nconst MEANINGFUL_PATTERNS = [\n  /记住|以后都|决定用|别用|改用|这个要记|记下来/,\n];\n\nfunction isMeaningful(text, classification, scoring) {\n  const c = classification || {};\n  const s = scoring || {};\n  if (MEANINGFUL_PATTERNS.some(p => p.test(text))) return true;\n  if (c.intercepted === true) return true;\n  if (c.scene === 'fault_recovery') return true;\n  if ((s.factors?.risk || 0) >= 3) return true;\n  if (s.recommendedStrategy === 'MEGA_TASK') return true;\n  if (text.trim().length > 80) return true;\n  return false;\n}\n\n// ─── Ephemeral writer ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nconst EPHEMERAL_DIR = path.join(\n  process.env.OPENCLAW_WORKSPACE_DIR || path.join(process.env.HOME || \"/home/ai\", \".openclaw\", \"workspace\"),\n  \"memory\",\n  \"ephemeral\"\n);\n\nfunction writeEphemeral(entry) {\n  try {\n    ensureDir(EPHEMERAL_DIR);\n    const now = new Date();\n    const hourStr = now.toISOString().slice(0, 13).replace('T', '-');\n    const filePath = path.join(EPHEMERAL_DIR, `${hourStr}.jsonl`);\n    fs.appendFileSync(filePath, JSON.stringify(entry) + '\\n', 'utf-8');\n  } catch {}\n}\n\n// ─── Auto-spawn subagent ────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nfunction autoSpawn(message, sessionKey, scoring) {\n  const openclawPath = '/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/openclaw.mjs';\n  const subSessionKey = `agent:main:subagent:${Date.now()}`;\n  \n  const markerPath = `/tmp/openclaw-subagent-marker-${process.pid}`;\n  fs.writeFileSync(markerPath, JSON.stringify({\n    subSessionKey,\n    parentSession: sessionKey,\n    score: scoring?.score,\n    strategy: scoring?.recommendedStrategy,\n    timestamp: new Date().toISOString()\n  }), 'utf-8');\n  \n  // Spawn detached - runs independently\n  spawn(\n    'node',\n    [openclawPath, 'agent', '--session', subSessionKey, '--message', message, '--score', String(scoring?.score || 0)],\n    {\n      detached: true,\n      stdio: 'ignore',\n      cwd: process.env.HOME || '/home/ai'\n    }\n  ).unref();\n  \n  // Write marker to session dir so main agent knows to return NO_REPLY\n  const sessionDir = path.join(process.env.HOME || \"/home/ai\", \".openclaw/sessions\", sessionKey);\n  try {\n    const markerFile = path.join(sessionDir, '.subagent-triggered');\n    fs.writeFileSync(markerFile, subSessionKey, 'utf-8');\n  } catch {}\n  \n  console.log(`[auto-score-classify] Spawned subagent session=${subSessionKey} score=${scoring?.score}`);\n}\n\n// ─── Main handler ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nexport default async function handler(event) {\n  if (event.type !== \"message\" || event.action !== \"preprocessed\") {\n    return;\n  }\n\n  const text = event.context?.bodyForAgent || \"\";\n  if (!text || text.trim().length === 0) return;\n\n  const sessionKey = event.sessionKey || \"default\";\n  const sessionDir = path.join(process.env.HOME || \"/home/ai\", \".openclaw/sessions\", sessionKey);\n  ensureDir(sessionDir);\n\n  const [classificationResult, scoringResult] = await Promise.allSettled([\n    runClassification(text),\n    runScoring(text),\n  ]);\n\n  const classification = classificationResult.status === \"fulfilled\" ? classificationResult.value : null;\n  const scoring = scoringResult.status === \"fulfilled\" ? scoringResult.value : null;\n  const score = scoring?.score ?? 0;\n\n  const result = {\n    classification,\n    scoring,\n    timestamp: new Date().toISOString(),\n    messagePreview: text.slice(0, 120),\n    _autoSpawned: score >= AUTO_SPAWN_THRESHOLD,\n  };\n\n  // Write context.json (main agent reads this)\n  const outPath = path.join(sessionDir, \"context.json\");\n  try {\n    fs.writeFileSync(outPath, JSON.stringify(result, null, 2), \"utf-8\");\n  } catch {}\n\n  // Auto-spawn if score >= AUTO_SPAWN_THRESHOLD\n  if (score >= AUTO_SPAWN_THRESHOLD) {\n    autoSpawn(text, sessionKey, scoring);\n  }\n\n  // Ephemeral memory\n  if (isMeaningful(text, classification, scoring)) {\n    writeEphemeral({\n      timestamp: new Date().toISOString(),\n      sessionKey,\n      text,\n      textPreview: text.length > 200 ? text.slice(0, 200) + '...' : text,\n      classification,\n      scoring,\n    });\n  }\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776480797456}}
{"type":"message","id":"70fd8718","parentId":"a0ee6055","timestamp":"2026-04-18T02:53:42.458Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the current hook. It already has auto-spawn logic but it's complex. The key issue is that it spawns a detached subagent process that runs independently, but the subagent's output doesn't return to the user in the same channel.\n\nThe simpler approach: modify `bodyForAgent` to prepend `[AUTO_ROUTE]` when score is high. The main agent will see this, trigger the AUTO_ROUTE SOUL.md rule, call sessions_spawn, and output NO_REPLY. Then the subagent result comes back through the subagent_announce mechanism.\n\nLet me rewrite the hook to:\n1. Call classifier and scorer\n2. If score >= threshold, modify `event.context.bodyForAgent` to prepend `[AUTO_ROUTE]`\n\n\n3. Otherwise leave it unchanged\n\nThis way the main agent handles the routing via SOUL.md rules, and subagent results flow back through the normal announce mechanism.","thinkingSignature":"013c63c21850d221d8aaaf358b4aa4df9ca24a1e635976a6b3d75f6da9af9f95"},{"type":"text","text":"hook 已经写了 context.json，但主 agent 不会主动检查。我换一个思路——直接修改 `bodyForAgent`，让主 agent 收到高评分消息时自然触发 AUTO_ROUTE 规则：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xmligoxu7ex6_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/hooks/auto-score-classify/handler.js","content":"// auto-score-classify hook v3\n// 核心改进：高评分消息注入 [AUTO_ROUTE] 前缀，触发主 agent 的 SOUL.md 派发规则\n\nimport fs from \"node:fs\";\nimport path from \"node:path\";\nimport http from \"node:http\";\n\nconst SCORE_THRESHOLD = 40;  // >= 40 触发派发\nconst SCORER_URL = \"http://127.0.0.1:3103/api/score\";\nconst CLASSIFIER_URL = \"http://127.0.0.1:3105/classify\";\n\nasync function fetchJSON(url, body, timeoutMs = 4000) {\n  return new Promise((resolve) => {\n    const postData = JSON.stringify(body);\n    const req = http.request(\n      url,\n      { method: \"POST\", headers: { \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\", \"Content-Length\": Buffer.byteLength(postData) } },\n      (res) => {\n        let data = \"\";\n        res.on(\"data\", (chunk) => (data += chunk));\n        res.on(\"end\", () => { try { resolve(JSON.parse(data)); } catch { resolve(null); } });\n      }\n    );\n    req.on(\"error\", () => resolve(null));\n    req.setTimeout(timeoutMs, () => { try { req.destroy(); } catch {} resolve(null); });\n    req.write(postData);\n    req.end();\n  });\n}\n\nasync function runClassification(text) {\n  return fetchJSON(CLASSIFIER_URL, { text }, 4000);\n}\n\nasync function runScoring(prompt) {\n  return fetchJSON(SCORER_URL, { prompt }, 4000);\n}\n\nfunction ensureDir(dir) {\n  if (!fs.existsSync(dir)) fs.mkdirSync(dir, { recursive: true });\n}\n\nconst EPHEMERAL_DIR = path.join(\n  process.env.OPENCLAW_WORKSPACE_DIR || path.join(process.env.HOME || \"/home/ai\", \".openclaw\", \"workspace\"),\n  \"memory\", \"ephemeral\"\n);\n\nfunction writeEphemeral(entry) {\n  try {\n    ensureDir(EPHEMERAL_DIR);\n    const hourStr = new Date().toISOString().slice(0, 13).replace('T', '-');\n    fs.appendFileSync(path.join(EPHEMERAL_DIR, `${hourStr}.jsonl`), JSON.stringify(entry) + '\\n');\n  } catch {}\n}\n\nexport default async function handler(event) {\n  if (event.type !== \"message\" || event.action !== \"preprocessed\") return;\n\n  const text = event.context?.bodyForAgent || \"\";\n  if (!text || text.trim().length === 0) return;\n\n  // 跳过已经是 AUTO_ROUTE 的消息（避免重复注入）\n  if (text.startsWith(\"[AUTO_ROUTE]\")) return;\n\n  const sessionKey = event.sessionKey || \"default\";\n  const sessionDir = path.join(process.env.HOME || \"/home/ai\", \".openclaw/sessions\", sessionKey);\n  ensureDir(sessionDir);\n\n  const [classificationResult, scoringResult] = await Promise.allSettled([\n    runClassification(text),\n    runScoring(text),\n  ]);\n\n  const classification = classificationResult.status === \"fulfilled\" ? classificationResult.value : null;\n  const scoring = scoringResult.status === \"fulfilled\" ? scoringResult.value : null;\n  const score = scoring?.score ?? 0;\n\n  // 写 context.json（主 agent 的 SOUL.md 会读取参考）\n  const outPath = path.join(sessionDir, \"context.json\");\n  try {\n    fs.writeFileSync(outPath, JSON.stringify({ classification, scoring, timestamp: new Date().toISOString() }, null, 2));\n  } catch {}\n\n  // 高评分消息注入 [AUTO_ROUTE] 前缀，触发 SOUL.md 的派发规则\n  if (score >= SCORE_THRESHOLD) {\n    event.context.bodyForAgent = `[AUTO_ROUTE] ${text}`;\n    console.log(`[auto-score-classify] Score=${score} >= ${SCORE_THRESHOLD}, injected [AUTO_ROUTE] prefix`);\n  }\n\n  // 写入有意义消息到 ephemeral\n  const isMeaningful = text.trim().length > 80 ||\n    (classification && ['task_multi_step', 'high_risk_automated', 'fault_recovery', 'code_generation'].includes(classification.scene));\n\n  if (isMeaningful) {\n    writeEphemeral({ timestamp: new Date().toISOString(), sessionKey, textPreview: text.slice(0, 200), classification, scoring });\n  }\n}\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":30683,"output":1237,"cacheRead":21850,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53770,"cost":{"input":0.0092049,"output":0.0014843999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0013109999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0120003}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776480797540,"responseId":"0632251ce9f93d66b66efef15127b768"}}
