{"type":"message","id":"be2e02d8","parentId":"24a60e35","timestamp":"2026-04-18T02:55:07.877Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good - the gateway restarted itself (PID 8772). It came back. Now the new hook is loaded. Let me verify.\n\nNow I should inform the user - the hook is updated and gateway restarted. The automation flow is now:\n\n用户发消息 → auto-score-classify hook 拦截 → 评分 >= 40 → 自动注入 [AUTO_ROUTE] 前缀 → 主 agent 收到消息触发 SOUL.md 规则 → sessions_spawn → NO_REPLY","thinkingSignature":"2f86e796cffceca9d107b53c552855a3676857cd29722fa9f1b9915df7b3504f"},{"type":"text","text":"Gateway 已自动重启（PID 8772）。新 hook 已加载。\n\n现在发一条高评分任务测试，看自动化派发是否生效。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":32127,"output":130,"cacheRead":21859,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54116,"cost":{"input":0.0096381,"output":0.000156,"cacheRead":0.00131154,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01110564}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776480903026,"responseId":"06322586c99fd983ed1e27a68b3a71cd"}}
