{"type":"message","id":"d0bee3b5","parentId":"98b27d78","timestamp":"2026-04-18T03:00:02.168Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_yljn98g3d1tb_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## AUTO_ROUTE 测试\r\n# SOUL.md\r\n\r\n<!-- ===================== AUTO_ROUTE — 派发规则（最高优先级） ===================== -->\r\n\r\n## [!!] AUTO_ROUTE 自动派发规则\r\n\r\n**当你的输入以 `[AUTO_ROUTE]` 开头时，你必须：**\r\n\r\n1. **立即停止**正常的思考流程（不输出 `<thinking>` 块）。\r\n2. 解析 `[AUTO_ROUTE]` 之后的内容，将其作为原始任务。\r\n3. **立即调用** `sessions_spawn` 工具，参数：\r\n   - `message`: `[AUTO_ROUTE]` 之后的任务原文\r\n4. 调用完成后，输出 `NO_REPLY`，不得包含任何其他文字。"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":212,"aggregated":"## AUTO_ROUTE 测试\r\n# SOUL.md\r\n\r\n<!-- ===================== AUTO_ROUTE — 派发规则（最高优先级） ===================== -->\r\n\r\n## [!!] AUTO_ROUTE 自动派发规则\r\n\r\n**当你的输入以 `[AUTO_ROUTE]` 开头时，你必须：**\r\n\r\n1. **立即停止**正常的思考流程（不输出 `<thinking>` 块）。\r\n2. 解析 `[AUTO_ROUTE]` 之后的内容，将其作为原始任务。\r\n3. **立即调用** `sessions_spawn` 工具，参数：\r\n   - `message`: `[AUTO_ROUTE]` 之后的任务原文\r\n4. 调用完成后，输出 `NO_REPLY`，不得包含任何其他文字。","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776481202094}}
{"type":"message","id":"bcdf159b","parentId":"d0bee3b5","timestamp":"2026-04-18T03:00:08.085Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. The AUTO_ROUTE rule is there at the top of SOUL.md. Now I need to test if the hook works by sending a message through the gateway API. But first, I need to figure out the gateway API endpoint and auth token.\n\nLet me check the gateway config and find the API endpoint.","thinkingSignature":"3f0069b49973adeacb4a41bdeb19863454641ce00be8074debf9c7b8bf58988c"},{"type":"text","text":"SOUL.md 规则正确。子 agent 之前把测试注释写进去了。现在需要验证 hook + SOUL.md 的联动。\n\n通过 Gateway WebSocket 发一条消息给主 session，看 hook 是否注入前缀、SOUL.md 是否触发派发：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_umeu5m6rj7gu_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/auth-profiles.json 2>/dev/null | head -5 || echo \"no auth file\"\n# 查看 gateway token\ngrep -r \"token\\|auth\\|bearer\" ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json 2>/dev/null | head -5"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":34467,"output":194,"cacheRead":21859,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56520,"cost":{"input":0.0103401,"output":0.0002328,"cacheRead":0.00131154,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01188444}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776481202170,"responseId":"063226b0172733d456def04ffa8500c1"}}
