{"type":"message","id":"fd4be20b","parentId":"85205da4","timestamp":"2026-04-18T03:04:54.130Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking \"what happened\" - they want a clear explanation of what just occurred. Let me summarize concisely.","thinkingSignature":"1423e1fa938bafb87fe9a034b1ec7a2524c8e193c9e1b1d8e5b0f500faf4ec1f"},{"type":"text","text":"**完整链路回顾**：\n\n| 步骤 | 发生了什么 |\n|------|-----------|\n| 1 | 我用 `sessions_send` 给主 session 发了 `[AUTO_ROUTE] 帮我写一个Python快速排序` |\n| 2 | 主 session 的 SOUL.md 检测到 `[AUTO_ROUTE]` 前缀 → **立即停止思考流程** |\n| 3 | 主 session **不生成任何回复**，直接调用 `sessions_spawn` 派发子 agent |\n| 4 | 主 session 输出 `NO_REPLY`（本轮无任何文字回复） |\n| 5 | 子 agent 收到任务 → 执行 → 写文件 → 返回结果 |\n| 6 | 子 agent 的结果通过 `subagent_announce` 推送到你看到的界面 |\n\n**你的感受**：只看到子 agent 的代码结果，没有看到我说任何废话。\n\n这就是我们设计的**自动化派发流程**——hook 评分 >= 40 → 注入前缀 → 主 agent 静默派发 → 子 agent 执行。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58,"output":242,"cacheRead":21859,"cacheWrite":35868,"totalTokens":58027,"cost":{"input":0.0000174,"output":0.0002904,"cacheRead":0.00131154,"cacheWrite":0.0134505,"total":0.015069840000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776481484970,"responseId":"063227cbb9e6496ba252c8563770b0ac"}}
