{"type":"message","id":"32c664c6","parentId":"b97c868d","timestamp":"2026-04-18T03:05:41.258Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking: do they need to manually add [AUTO_ROUTE] to their messages?\n\nThe answer is NO - the hook (auto-score-classify) is supposed to automatically inject the [AUTO_ROUTE] prefix for high-scoring messages. The user doesn't need to add it manually.\n\nThe design is:\n- User sends normal message\n- Hook intercepts → calls classifier (3105) + scorer (3103)\n- If score >= 40, hook automatically prepends [AUTO_ROUTE] to the message\n- Main agent then sees [AUTO_ROUTE] and triggers the dispatch flow\n\nSo [AUTO_ROUTE] is added AUTOMATICALLY by the hook, not manually by the user.\n\n\nThe only time the user would need to add it manually is if they want to force dispatch for a message that scored below the threshold, or if they're testing in an environment where the hook isn't active yet.","thinkingSignature":"fbdc548d580948ac0015ad08d70ee301105a0ba450f7d087010fecfe429e0fcc"},{"type":"text","text":"**不需要**。\n\nHook 会自动判断：\n\n```\n你发普通消息 → hook 拦截 → 评分 >= 40 → 自动注入 [AUTO_ROUTE]\n你发普通消息 → hook 拦截 → 评分 < 40 → 不注入 → 我正常处理\n```\n\n手动加 `[AUTO_ROUTE]` 只用于：\n1. 测试验证\n2. 强制派发一个低分消息（你自己确定要派发）"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58,"output":283,"cacheRead":57812,"cacheWrite":197,"totalTokens":58350,"cost":{"input":0.0000174,"output":0.00033959999999999996,"cacheRead":0.00346872,"cacheWrite":0.000073875,"total":0.003899595}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776481530531,"responseId":"063227f96d7690e5f828fe257b6cb505"}}
