{"type":"message","id":"0241ecad","parentId":"e3d171e5","timestamp":"2026-04-18T03:07:35.317Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if it's really true that the hook will automatically inject [AUTO_ROUTE] for high-scoring messages. Let me verify - did we actually confirm that the hook is working and injecting the prefix?\n\nThe last test was:\n1. I manually sent [AUTO_ROUTE] via sessions_send (not hook injection)\n2. The main agent received it and matched the SOUL.md rule\n3. The main agent spawned a subagent and returned NO_REPLY\n\nBut we never confirmed that the hook actually injects [AUTO_ROUTE] for regular user messages. The hook writes context.json and adds a marker, but does it actually modify bodyForAgent?\n \nLooking back at the hook code, it does attempt to modify bodyForAgent directly, but this requires the event.context object to be mutable - if it's passed by value rather than reference, the modification won't actually take effect. And even if it does work, there's a deeper question: if the body gets modified with [AUTO_ROUTE], does the main agent's SOUL.md rules actually get re-evaluated after that modification, or is the rules matching already locked in?\n\nThe real issue is that I've been testing with messages I sent through sessions_send, not real user messages through the gateway, so I haven't actually confirmed the hook is doing what it's supposed to do. The gateway likely doesn't even pass bodyForAgent to hooks - it probably only sends event metadata, not the message body itself. So the hook probably can't modify messages at all, and the whole approach might be fundamentally broken.","thinkingSignature":"9e5c56993862d48af2a63b9d3d318d68b0e34903781b497ad84ea2e4fa349483"},{"type":"text","text":"**需要诚实地回答：不确定。**\n\n我们刚才验证的是：**SOUL.md 的 AUTO_ROUTE 规则 + sessions_spawn 联动**——这个链路是通的。\n\n但 **hook 是否真的注入了前缀**，从未验证过。我们没有在真实用户消息到网关时检查过 hook 是否修改了 `bodyForAgent`。\n\n**最大的未知**：`event.context.bodyForAgent` 在 gateway → hook 的调用链里是**引用传递还是值拷贝**？如果是值拷贝，hook 的修改不会生效。\n\n**现状**：\n- SOUL.md AUTO_ROUTE + sessions_spawn：✅ 已验证\n- Hook 自动注入 [AUTO_ROUTE]：⚠️ 未验证\n\n要真正验证 hook，需要在 gateway 收到用户消息时打日志看 `bodyForAgent` 的值。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58,"output":486,"cacheRead":57974,"cacheWrite":185,"totalTokens":58703,"cost":{"input":0.0000174,"output":0.0005832,"cacheRead":0.0034784399999999997,"cacheWrite":0.000069375,"total":0.004148415}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776481634768,"responseId":"063228623ccd1c82bee489274ed35fcb"}}
