{"type":"message","id":"c7b5a944","parentId":"30ec0709","timestamp":"2026-04-18T03:24:43.832Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me give a concise status update. After extensive investigation, I found:\n\n1. `auto-score-classify` hook was NOT registered in `hooks.internal.entries` - I added it to the config\n2. The hook handler uses ES modules (`import`) but OpenClaw's internal hook system expects CommonJS or a different format\n3. The hook is loaded from `~/.openclaw/hooks/auto-score-classify/` but gateway looks for it via workspace hook discovery\n\nThe key insight from reading the gateway code: hooks are loaded via `loadWorkspaceHookEntries` which reads `HOOK.md` from hook directories and loads the handler. My hook IS in the right place (`~/.openclaw/hooks/`), but the issue is whether that directory is being scanned.\n\n\nI need to verify whether `~/.openclaw/hooks/` is actually included in the workspace hook discovery path.","thinkingSignature":"9b251d7d903fc600f45eeaa03a529569804ffe1660e4eafe351c9fed80ead183"},{"type":"text","text":"花了很久追踪代码。总结：\n\n**Hook 系统加载流程**：\n1. Gateway 启动 → `loadInternalHooks()` → 从 workspace 扫描 hook 目录\n2. 扫描 `~/.openclaw/workspace/hooks/`（不是 `~/.openclaw/hooks/`）\n3. 然后才加载 `hooks.internal.entries` 里注册的名字\n\n**问题**：`~/.openclaw/hooks/auto-score-classify/` 不在 gateway 的扫描路径里。\n\n让我确认 workspace hooks 目录：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_simsf1xcxa4u_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace/hooks/ 2>/dev/null || echo \"NOT EXISTS\"\n# 也检查 workspace 里的 hooks 软链接\nfind ~/.openclaw/workspace -name \"hooks\" -type d 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58,"output":355,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":77259,"totalTokens":77672,"cost":{"input":0.0000174,"output":0.000426,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.028972125,"total":0.029415525}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776482668748,"responseId":"06322c6db58b90a13