{"type":"message","id":"7faac69c","parentId":"3b18a22e","timestamp":"2026-04-18T03:28:46.601Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"3103 (scorer) is not running! Only 3105 (classifier) is running. This explains why the score was 0 - the hook tried to call 3103 but got no response (or a fallback 0), so score defaulted to 0.\n\nThat's the issue. Let me restart the scorer (v8_scorer).","thinkingSignature":"e514e92213cf8487313fb6542fc5316c6a67441aa72d769c1aa3901ee94c20f3"},{"type":"text","text":"**找到问题**：3103 scorer 已崩溃，只剩 3105 分类器在跑。\n\n这就是为什么评分全是 0。重启 scorer：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_edvffbanlm5o_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find ~/.openclaw -name \"*.sh\" -o -name \"start*\" 2>/dev/null | xargs grep -l \"3103\\|scorer\" 2>/dev/null | head -5\n# 找 scorer 启动脚本\nfind ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills -name \"*.sh\" -o -name \"start*\" 2>/dev/null | head -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":62055,"output":209,"cacheRead":21865,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84129,"cost":{"input":0.018616499999999998,"output":0.00025079999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0013119,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.020179199999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776482919091,"responseId":"06322d67f5a7b18d565a134f8e2c77cc"}}
