{"type":"message","id":"49b8f35e","parentId":"eea2595c","timestamp":"2026-04-18T03:30:27.826Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The scoring engine works, but it only scores 24 for that complex message! The issue is that the scoring logic (regex-based) doesn't capture the true complexity of the task \"分析所有hook代码并生成文档\". The regex patterns for \"分析\" have a weight of 1 in the `duration` factor, and there are no patterns matching \"hook\" or \"文档\" or \"架构\", so the score is very low.\n\nSo the scorer itself is working correctly, but the patterns are not comprehensive enough. For \"分析 ~/.openclaw 目录下所有 hook 代码，生成 Hook 系统架构文档\" - the patterns that match:\n- \"分析\" -> duration +1\n\n\n- \"代码\" -> not in any pattern\n- \"文档\" -> not in any pattern\n- \"架构\" -> architecture has weight 2 but it's \"架构\" not \"architecture\"\n- \"hook\" -> not in any pattern\n- \"生成\" -> not in any pattern\n\nThe patterns are too limited and English-focused, missing Chinese terms like \"分析\" that should trigger higher complexity scores.\n\nEven though the message clearly involves multi-file analysis and documentation generation, the scorer only returns 24, which falls into the DIRECT strategy range. To fix this, I need to either add more Chinese patterns to the scoring engine or lower the threshold from 40 to 20.\n\nActually, I'm realizing the hook is working as intended—it successfully calls the scorer and returns a result. The real issue is that the scoring engine's pattern matching isn't robust enough for Chinese text. So the approach should be: fix the scorer itself to better handle Chinese patterns, keep the threshold at 40, and potentially use the classifier's `task_multi_step` label to inject `[AUTO_ROUTE]` when the scorer score is unreliable. But the classifier at 3105 appears to be down as well.\n\nLet me verify that 3105 is actually running.","thinkingSignature":"5d477516b268ef55a846aad6475e529fef1479b974879f09af3d618256bb587a"},{"type":"text","text":"Scoring 引擎能跑，但评分只有 24 分——问题在于 scorer 的中文 pattern 太少，不匹配\"分析\"、\"hook\"、\"文档\"等关键词。\n\n同时 3105 分类器也在跑，说明它也返回了 0 分。让我验证 scorer 和分类器的实时状态：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xm1q0bqqr66c_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3105/classify -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"text\":\"分析 ~/.openclaw 目录下所有 hook 代码，生成架构文档\"}' --max-time 3"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":72060,"output":520,"cacheRead":21865,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94445,"cost":{"input":0.021618,"output":0.000624,"cacheRead":0.0013119,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0235539}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776483012580,"responseId":"06322dc35e74a39f23a8129fe963517e"}}
