{"type":"message","id":"a260aa3b","parentId":"be0d654c","timestamp":"2026-04-18T03:35:21.507Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to know what problems were discovered. Let me give a concise summary of the key issues found during the hook system investigation.","thinkingSignature":"8c25f80d86ec008ca3044d370bcf8e18c5f1a4f341208089c784d6f30739716e"},{"type":"text","text":"**三大问题**：\n\n1. **Hook 从未加载** — `auto-score-classify` 在 `~/.openclaw/hooks/`，但 gateway 只扫描 `~/.openclaw/workspace/hooks/`。花了很久追踪才发现这个路径差异。\n\n2. **3103 scorer 服务不存在** — 评分引擎代码在 `v8/src/scoring/scoring.js`，但没有 HTTP 服务包装。Hook 调用 `localhost:3103` 永远失败，导致评分全为 0。\n\n3. **Hook 注入 vs Agent 执行的时序问题** — 即使 hook 注入了 `[AUTO_ROUTE]` 前缀，Agent 也需要 SOUL.md 里有对应规则才能触发派发。这个链路昨晚才通过修改 SOUL.md 解决。\n\n---\n\n**根本原因**：文档描述的架构（v8 router、task orchestrator 内置路由）在这个环境里从未真正部署，都是历史代码+外部服务拼凑的。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58,"output":222,"cacheRead":21865,"cacheWrite":75303,"totalTokens":97448,"cost":{"input":0.0000174,"output":0.00026639999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0013119,"cacheWrite":0.028238625,"total":0.029834325}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776483309091,"responseId":"06322eed3c975fbad28d6e806ab58666"}}
