{"type":"message","id":"6161e2b1","parentId":"e85ffe97","timestamp":"2026-04-18T03:36:50.887Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_cjkbkpomcz9l_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[scorer] v8 scoring server running on http://0.0.0.0:3103\n[scorer] Endpoint: POST /api/score { prompt: \"...\" }\n{\"score\":41,\"factors\":{\"logic\":2,\"risk\":0,\"duration\":1,\"resource\":0,\"uncertainty\":0,\"dependency\":0},\"recommendedStrategy\":\"SPAWN_SUBAGENT\",\"timeout\":120,\"_raw\":{\"total\":3,\"max\":18}}[scorer] SIGTERM, shutting down"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3063,"aggregated":"[scorer] v8 scoring server running on http://0.0.0.0:3103\n[scorer] Endpoint: POST /api/score { prompt: \"...\" }\n{\"score\":41,\"factors\":{\"logic\":2,\"risk\":0,\"duration\":1,\"resource\":0,\"uncertainty\":0,\"dependency\":0},\"recommendedStrategy\":\"SPAWN_SUBAGENT\",\"timeout\":120,\"_raw\":{\"total\":3,\"max\":18}}[scorer] SIGTERM, shutting down","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776483410815}}
{"type":"message","id":"19855094","parentId":"6161e2b1","timestamp":"2026-04-18T03:36:57.959Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The scorer server works and returns `score: 41` with `recommendedStrategy: SPAWN_SUBAGENT`. This is great - it means the message \"分析 ~/.openclaw 目录下所有 hook 代码，生成架构文档\" gets a score of 41, which is >= 40 and would trigger the AUTO_ROUTE injection.\n\nNow I need to:\n1. Set it up as a systemd user service\n2. Start it so it persists\n\nLet me set up a systemd user service for it.","thinkingSignature":"15621bd4b0f2cd419fd2a30e425b97c9d5f1ff9150bcb85a2b386c3e700e87d4"},{"type":"text","text":"**Scorer 服务正常！** 评分 41，触发阈值。现在写成 systemd user service：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_e1383ra8sixc_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.systemd/user/openclaw-scorer.service","content":"[Unit]\nDescription=OpenClaw v8 Scoring Server (port 3103)\nAfter=network.target\n\n[Service]\nType=simple\nWorkingDirectory=/home/ai/.openclaw/v8\nExecStart=/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/node scripts/scorer-server.js\nRestart=on-failure\nRestartSec=5\nEnvironment=NODE_ENV=production\nEnvironment=PORT=3103\n\n# Logging\nStandardOutput=append:/home/ai/.openclaw/logs/scorer.log\nStandardError=append:/home/ai/.openclaw/logs/scorer.log\n\n[Install]\nWantedBy=default.target\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":77253,"output":311,"cacheRead":21865,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99429,"cost":{"input":0.0231759,"output":0.00037319999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0013119,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.024861}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776483410891,"responseId":"06322f51be713eed4399b6d479a39853"}}
