{"type":"message","id":"447ec8cc","parentId":"95905d51","timestamp":"2026-04-18T03:54:31.199Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The hook is still returning SCORE: 0 for the message \"分析 ~/.openclaw/hooks 目录下所有 hook 的功能、依赖和调用关系，生成一份完整架构文档\". But the scorer at 3103 works when called directly!\n\nWait - the hook is calling 3103 but still getting 0. Let me check if the hook is actually reaching the scorer at 3103 or if it's calling the wrong endpoint. The hook's `runScoring` function uses `http://127.0.0.1:3103/api/score`. But wait, the scorer I started is listening on 0.0.0.0:3103. Let me test directly.\n\nActually wait - the log shows `SCORE: 0 (threshold=40)` and `NO INJECTION`. This means the hook IS being called and IS calling the scorer, but getting score 0. Earlier the direct curl test returned 41. So why does the hook get 0?\n\nLet me test directly with curl to see what the scorer returns for this specific Chinese text.","thinkingSignature":"b2ca646758d8d465df17964486448b54482159bdadd40439269a374d0bd1b972"},{"type":"text","text":"Hook 调用 scorer 返回 0，但直接 curl 返回 41。说明 scorer 端点或传参有问题。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_h4xvfnr5pasd_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 直接测试 scorer 对这条中文消息的评分\ncurl -s -X POST http://localhost:3103/api/score -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"prompt\":\"分析 ~/.openclaw/hooks 目录下所有 hook 的功能、依赖和调用关系，生成一份完整架构文档\"}' --max-time 3"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":79451,"output":339,"cacheRead":21865,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101655,"cost":{"input":0.0238353,"output":0.00040679999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0013119,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.025554}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776484461317,"responseId":"0632336c728c91102d8816525bbbcad7"}}
