{"type":"message","id":"f321ede5","parentId":"5beab7fa","timestamp":"2026-04-18T04:12:01.129Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No history file. The subagent session might not have been persisted, or it used a different session key. Let me check recent sessions.Actually, the subagent ran in `agent:main:subagent:a020f027` but the result was supposed to be pushed via `subagent_announce` to the webchat channel. The fact that the user sent \"？\" means they didn't see the result in webchat.\n\nThe issue might be that the subagent_announce mechanism works but the user's webchat didn't receive it, OR the subagent never actually completed successfully.\n\nLet me check the openclaw tasks to see if the subagent completed.","thinkingSignature":"d28e6b4a70fa224bc1cf5eed9baaa386bf19922626ca6c71bada6d09fdd9704f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ztc1quj2ajl5_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/sessions/agent:main:subagent:/ 2>/dev/null | tail -5\nfind ~/.openclaw/sessions -name \"*.json\" -newer /tmp/openclaw/openclaw-2026-04-18.log 2>/dev/null | head -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":108216,"output":218,"cacheRead":21865,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130299,"cost":{"input":0.0324648,"output":0.00026159999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0013119,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0340383}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776485512977,"responseId":"063237889a10bc705dbf8ec6171f2443"}}
