{"type":"message","id":"b47a790d","parentId":"980bfc45","timestamp":"2026-04-18T04:25:41.782Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is frustrated - they've been burned multiple times by my reckless modifications. They're right to call me out. Let me think carefully before acting.\n\nThe current state:\n1. Gateway PID 10539 is running\n2. I just killed it and tried to restart\n3. The exec command shows a \"missing tool result\" which suggests the command may have failed\n\nLet me check the actual state right now - is the gateway still running? Did the restart work?\n\nThen I need to carefully think about what the user wants vs what I'm about to do:\n\n**What the user wants**: Deploy context-monitor hook properly\n**What I've done**: \n1. Wrote handler.js - this is fine\n2. Added context config to openclaw.json - this is fine\n3. Tried to restart gateway - UNCERTAIN if this worked\n\n**What I should do before touching anything**:\n1. First check current gateway status - is it running or did I break it?\n2. If it's down, restart it carefully\n3. Then verify the hook loads without crashing gateway\n\nLet me check the gateway status first with a conservative approach.","thinkingSignature":"773a8e0df5877f21dba88e947038a877aaec4e364e40c30c46468925f3fc2011"},{"type":"text","text":"### 思考\n\n**教训**：我刚才没有确认 gateway 重启是否成功就继续操作——这是搞坏系统的典型方式。\n\n**现在必须先做什么**：检查 gateway 当前真实状态，不能假设它还在运行。\n\n**新 hook 的风险**：context-monitor 操作 `context.json` 文件，有写入风险。但如果配置正确，只在超限时才写入，风险可控。\n\n**行动步骤**：\n1. 先查 gateway 现状（死活）\n2. 若已死，谨慎重启\n3. 确认稳定后，再验证 hook 加载\n\n给我一分钟检查。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_py8qbov1yrgu_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ps aux | grep openclaw-gateway | grep -v grep\necho \"---\"\nss -tlnp 2>/dev/null | grep 18789"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58,"output":402,"cacheRead":55292,"cacheWrite":1905,"totalTokens":57657,"cost":{"input":0.0000174,"output":0