{"type":"message","id":"a47fc1f4","parentId":"30aa845d","timestamp":"2026-04-18T04:25:56.197Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Key error: `Hook 'context-monitor' has no events defined in metadata`\n\nThe HOOK.md for context-monitor doesn't have proper metadata events defined. I wrote the handler correctly but the HOOK.md metadata is missing or incomplete.\n\nLet me check the current HOOK.md for context-monitor.","thinkingSignature":"0c834cc145295d9cdf1299dba9c460cf4af06ac6df78021f776b25a9f0c76df3"},{"type":"text","text":"两个问题：\n\n1. `Hook 'context-monitor' has no events defined in metadata` — HOOK.md 元数据不完整\n2. `Handler 'default' from context-monitor is not a function` — gateway 重启时加载的是旧版 handler\n\n先看 HOOK.md：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jaeedw5v5f3o_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/hooks/context-monitor/HOOK.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":38348,"output":163,"cacheRead":21865,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60376,"cost":{"input":0.0115044,"output":0.00019559999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0013119,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0130119}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776486351820,"responseId":"06323ace7c657ec9c981ed78bc5a6966"}}
