{"type":"message","id":"4dd8bf6c","parentId":"d2c308ad","timestamp":"2026-04-18T04:26:10.283Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The HOOK.md looks correct. The problem is that the gateway was started with the OLD handler.js (before my write). The new handler.js was written AFTER the last gateway restart. So the gateway loaded the old (CJS/broken) handler.\n\nI need to check the HOOK.md more carefully. The error says \"no events defined in metadata\" - but I can see events are defined. This might be a parsing issue with the YAML frontmatter.\n\nWait - looking at the HOOK.md content above, the YAML frontmatter is missing the `---` delimiters! It's missing the opening `---`. That's the problem.","thinkingSignature":"6b9a38428ec4c089553c2289295b08e48a8bfb69b9b9acaa7f9e0d575a4f7018"},{"type":"text","text":"问题找到了：HOOK.md 的 YAML frontmatter **缺少 `---` 分隔符**，gateway 解析不到 metadata 事件定义。\n\ngateway 重启时加载的是我写入新 handler.js **之前**的旧版本，所以报错 `not a function`。新代码已经落盘，但需要 gateway **再次重启**才能生效。\n\n**关键判断**：这次重启是必要的——旧版 handler 是坏掉的 CJS 脚本，不重启反而持续报错。不重启 gateway 新代码永远无法加载。\n\n**行动**：重启 gateway，分两步确认：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jxu1fmc3dk1f_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 确认新 handler.js 已经落盘且语法正确\nnode --input-type=module < /home/ai/.openclaw/hooks/context-monitor/handler.js 2>&1 | head -5\necho \"---\"\n# 确认 HOOK.md 有正确的 frontmatter\nhead -3 /home/ai/.openclaw/hooks/context-monitor/HOOK.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":38619,"output":341,"cacheRead":21865,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60825,"cost":{"input":0.011585699999999999,"output":0.00040919999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0013119,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.013306799999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776486356631,"responseId":"06323ad42fd35dd2b9a029db7d983ce3"}}
