{"type":"message","id":"cb5299b8","parentId":"ed49cf44","timestamp":"2026-04-18T04:26:25.158Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The HOOK.md is missing the `---` frontmatter delimiters! It's just raw YAML without the standard Jekyll-style delimiters. Let me fix this by adding the proper delimiters.","thinkingSignature":"2a027e545cb778c63103129d21ac00cba3534cc10de041b3a5806238dae2e044"},{"type":"text","text":"确认：HOOK.md **没有 `---` 分隔符**， gateway YAML 解析器无法识别它为有效 frontmatter，导致 `no events defined in metadata`。\n\n修复 HOOK.md，加上标准 frontmatter 分隔符：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vt822oa0ld8m_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/hooks/context-monitor/HOOK.md","content":"---\nname: context-monitor\ndescription: \"监控 session context 大小，超过阈值时触发自动压缩。依赖 context.maxContextTokens 和 summarizeThreshold 配置。\"\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\": {\n      \"emoji\": \"🧠\",\n      \"events\": [\"message:preprocessed\", \"agent:response\"],\n      \"requires\": {\"bins\": [\"node\"], \"config\": [\"context\"]},\n      \"always\": true\n    }\n  }\n---\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":39426,"output":228,"cacheRead":21865,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61519,"cost":{"input":0.0118278,"output":0.0002736,"cacheRead":0.0013119,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0134133}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776486380738,"responseId":"06323aebc2a08aec752347e156933bdc"}}
