{"type":"message","id":"cb56adec","parentId":"f5f6dcf5","timestamp":"2026-04-18T04:26:42.341Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to restart the gateway. But the user said \"不准搞坏openclaw\". I need to be careful. Let me think about what the risks are:\n\n1. The gateway is currently running with the OLD (broken) context-monitor handler - it errored on load\n2. The gateway already has 6 handlers loaded and is running fine\n3. Restarting will reload ALL hooks - if any hook is broken, it could crash the gateway\n\nWhat are the risks of restarting?\n- Gateway restart is a normal operation (I've done it many times before)\n- The openclaw.json backup is at ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json.bak4\n- If something goes wrong, I can kill and restart again\n\n\n- The auto-score-classify hook is working fine with its ESM handler, so that should survive the reload\n- context-monitor has been fixed with proper ESM and frontmatter, so it should load correctly now\n- The other hooks shouldn't be affected by the restart\n\nThe real question is whether I should restart at all. The user's explicit request was to deploy context-monitor, but the current gateway state has the broken CJS handler still loaded. Without restarting, the new code won't be picked up. Given that my previous restarts haven't caused issues and the backup is available, the risk seems manageable.\n\nNow I'm thinking through a safer approach: instead of a full gateway restart, I could use `openclaw gateway restart` which is the intended way to do this and should handle reloading hooks properly. Though I'm second-guessing whether this command actually reloads hook code or just restarts the process.\n\nActually, the most reliable path forward is to restart the gateway since I have backups, the context-monitor hook changes are ready, and the system has survived restarts before. I'll do it now, but I should give the user a clear warning that I'm about to restart.","thinkingSignature":"231edb15c89167e45d166ddf0d577958b1255109f6a4ba19d41700303687bab4"},{"type":"text","text":"现在 gateway 正在用旧版（坏掉的）handler 工作。**需要重启**才能让新代码生效——这是部署 hook 的必要步骤，不重启新代码永远不会被加载。\n\n**风险可控**：有配置文件备份，系统之前重启都成功。这次重启替换的是 context-monitor 一个 hook，其他 5 个不受影响。\n\n执行：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3o6y8s2rggjo_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw gateway restart 2>&1; echo \"EXIT: $?\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":39692,"output":503,"cacheRead":21865,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62060,"cost":{"input":0.011907599999999999,"output":0.0006035999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0013119,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.013823099999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776486385616,"responseId":"06323af14ab050b0ceab403c615f16ca"}}
