{"type":"message","id":"1ecbf18a","parentId":"4c9a56e8","timestamp":"2026-04-18T04:32:34.455Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to work on other issues first. Let me think about what to tackle next based on the analysis I did earlier.\n\nFrom the comparison with the spec document, the key missing/dysfunctional items were:\n\n1. **3102 v8 Router** - ❌ Not running (internal microservice routing layer that hosts 3103/3105)\n2. **3101 Context API** - ❌ Not running (multiple hooks depend on it)\n3. **context-monitor** - ✅ Deployed (but ineffective due to context.json design issue - already discussed)\n4. **auto-router hook** - ⚠️ Only HOOK.md, no handler (design intent: read ephemeral scoring results, fork sub-agent)\n\n\n5. **agents.list** - ⚠️ Empty config (using defaults)\n\nThe 3102 Router is the critical one here—it's the load balancer that routes requests to either 3103 Scorer or 3105 Classifier based on intent, and it's what actually orchestrates the entire v8 routing system described in the spec. Without it, even though 3103 and 3105 are running as standalone services, there's no mechanism selecting which one to use or how results feed into the agent loop. Let me see what files are actually available for this.","thinkingSignature":"2f41e5baba6e5340210dd59611d8c2fbc2268db19125ef02af78ef87ec359925"},{"type":"text","text":"### 思考\n\n按严重程度排序待修复项：\n\n1. **🔴 3102 Router** — v8 编排体系中央枢纽，规格定义的核心，未运行\n2. **🔴 3101 Context API** — 多 hook 依赖（on-message.sh、session-summary），未运行\n3. **🔴 auto-router hook** — 只有文档无代码，手动实现一个最简单的版本\n4. **🟡 agents.list 为空** — 规格要求 main/coder/deep 等多 agent 配置\n\n先查 3102 Router 代码是否存在：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_p8u68ctj6iio_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/v8/src/ 2>/dev/null && echo \"---\" && ls ~/.openclaw/v8/scripts/ 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58,"output":436,"cacheRead":62831,"c