{"type":"message","id":"3884fa97","parentId":"ae4bc1c0","timestamp":"2026-04-18T04:35:26.414Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"`agent:preparing` is not used in the gateway. This means the auto-router hook would never fire even if I implement it. So implementing auto-router on `agent:preparing` would be pointless.\n\nLet me think about a different approach. What events are actually supported? From the log earlier, we saw:\n- `message:preprocessed` ✅ (auto-score-classify works)\n- `command:new` ✅ (session-summary works)\n- `command:reset` ✅ (session-summary works)\n- `agent:bootstrap` ✅ (self-improvement works)\n- `agent:response` (maybe?)\n\nSince `agent:preparing` doesn't fire, auto-router can't work as designed. \n\nBut I could implement auto-router to use `message:preprocessed` instead—the spec describes it as reading ephemeral data and forking a sub-agent when the score is high enough, with the main agent returning a \"task submitted\" message. The existing hook already handles the fork-and-NO_REPLY pattern through [AUTO_ROUTE] injection. What auto-router could add is reading the actual score from ephemeral to make a smarter decision, rather than the current approach.\n\nThe issue is that if I make auto-router listen on `message:preprocessed`, it would compete with auto-score-classify—both would try to handle the same event. The simplest solution is to make auto-router a backup: if auto-score-classify didn't inject [AUTO_ROUTE], auto-router reads the ephemeral score and injects it if needed. Since auto-score-classify is currently force-injecting everything, auto-router would be dormant unless I switch auto-score-classify back to a scoring-based approach. But given that the user's main goal is just having the system work, maybe the better path forward is to keep auto-score-classify as-is and use auto-router only if auto-score-classify fails.\n\nLet me verify what events are actually firing in the gateway to understand the competition better.","thinkingSignature":"3e6b9dee8b893de99a896ce26f9bb03c06f486c85dfe15c5025a77a94178c128"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_j55ryxw960nl_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep \"fireAndForgetHook\\|createInternalHookEvent\" /home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/*.js 2>/dev/null | grep -v \".map:\" | head -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":52075,"output":475,"cacheRead":21865,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74415,"cost":{"input":0.0156225,"output":0.00057,"cacheRead":0.0013119,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0175044}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776486912395,"responseId":"06323d00d0ac76d5c9e971e4cdfe5b20"}}
