{"type":"message","id":"f06220aa","parentId":"b1a6b896","timestamp":"2026-04-18T04:37:37.041Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Key findings from the logs:\n\n1. **Gateway restarted at 12:36** - loaded 7 internal hook handlers ✅\n2. **New hook is running** - the 12:37 log entry shows `SCORE: 0 (threshold=40) strategy=DIRECT` - this is the new v9 hook logging format, not the old \"force mode\" format. The new hook IS working!\n3. But the score is 0 for \"先解决其它问题\" - this is a short message, so it correctly scores 0. The old hook would have injected AUTO_ROUTE, but the new one correctly skips it.\n\n\n4. **The new hook is functioning as intended** - it's properly scoring messages and making routing decisions based on the actual content length and complexity, rather than blindly injecting AUTO_ROUTE like the old version did.\n\nThe hook is now live and working correctly. Now I need to identify what's actually failing and fix it systematically.","thinkingSignature":"62d58079c847e92abdcea5e4788019286310741d2187a2ab2a7e1597ffce4387"},{"type":"text","text":"新 hook 工作了！关键证据：\n\n- `SCORE: 0 (threshold=40) strategy=DIRECT` — **新版本**的评分日志（之前强制模式只打印 `INJECTED [AUTO_ROUTE] (force mode)`）\n- 短消息 `\"先解决其它问题\"` 正确得分 0，**没有**强制注入\n\n现在 3101、3102、auto-router 的问题：\n\n| 缺口 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| **3101 Context API** | ✅ 刚启动，端口 3101 正常 |\n| **3102 Router** | 🔴 有代码但缺 express 依赖，无法启动 |\n| **auto-router hook** | ⚠️ `agent:preparing` 事件不存在，设计失效，auto-score-classify 已覆盖其职能 |\n\n**3102 为什么不能简单启动**：它依赖 `express` 模块（已在 openclaw 全局 node_modules 里），但 `~/.openclaw/v8/` 没有 `package.json` 来声明这个依赖。需要给 v8 写一个 package.json 才能正常启动。\n\n先确认 3102 启动需要什么：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_j9cslceosoif_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/v8/src/index.js | grep -E \"require\\(|listen\\(\" | head -15"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54146,"output":478,"cacheRead":21865,"cacheWrite"