{"type":"message","id":"cc94af7f","parentId":"5e75bd00","timestamp":"2026-04-18T04:37:57.663Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Beyond express, it also needs sqlite3. The v8 system has a lot of dependencies that aren't installed in the openclaw global node_modules. Installing these dependencies is non-trivial.\n\nLet me think about this differently. The 3102 Router is the v8 orchestrator which has many components (TaskStore, Scheduler, Executor, SecurityGateway, etc.). Installing all these dependencies properly would be complex.\n\nThe key question: **is the 3102 Router actually needed for the v8 routing system to work?** \n\nLooking at the architecture:\n- 3102 Router is described as the \"内部微服务路由层\" that hosts 3103/3105\n\n\n- But 3103 scorer and 3105 classifier are already running as standalone services\n- The auto-score-classify hook calls 3103 directly\n- So the 3102 Router might be an older architecture that's been replaced by standalone services\n\nI should check if there's a way to run just the router/api component without all the other dependencies, or if the standalone services already make the 3102 Router redundant.","thinkingSignature":"f7d89e427ab324fd2ae92604c9e12bce5914acfd866310978aded42703911f42"},{"type":"text","text":"3102 需要 sqlite3 等多个依赖，全部装好很复杂。**关键判断**：3103 scorer 和 3105 classifier 已经独立运行，auto-score-classify hook 直接调 3103。3102 Router 作为\"路由层\"可能已经是**过时的设计**，被 hook 方案替代了。\n\n先跳过 3102，确认当前真实跑通的状态：\n\n**现在已部署完毕且正常工作的**：\n- ✅ Gateway（18789）\n- ✅ 3103 Scorer\n- ✅ 3101 Context API（刚启动）\n- ✅ auto-score-classify hook（新 v9，基于真实评分）\n- ✅ context-monitor hook（已加载，虽然 context.json 不落地）\n\n**仍缺失**：\n- 🔴 3102 Router（依赖缺失，设计可能已过时）\n- 🔴 agents.list 配置（空，用默认单 agent）\n- ⚠️ session-summary 链路（/new 时应触发，今日未测试）\n\n你在 webchat 发一条 `[AUTO_ROUTE] 帮我写一个快速排序`，验证新 hook 评分派发是否正常："}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":55269,"output":440,"cacheRead":21865,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":7