{"type":"message","id":"d7f041be","parentId":"7c8408c5","timestamp":"2026-04-18T04:38:57.496Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is right - I should not ask them to test. I should test it myself. Let me send a message via sessions_send to trigger the hook and verify the new scoring-based dispatch works.","thinkingSignature":"a4151db7e74c9c1b7a6a2428c58a6ff7000c5f642ce2e78f61ce230165b5ea2e"},{"type":"text","text":"### 思考\n\n用户说得对。我来自己验证，不依赖用户操作。用 sessions_send 触发 hook，看它是否正确评分并决定是否派发。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_anx41ctebuxo_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 测试 scorer 对\"写一个Python快速排序\"的评分\ncurl -s -X POST http://127.0.0.1:3103/api/score -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"text\":\"帮我写一个Python快速排序\"}' 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":158,"cacheRead":77049,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77207,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0.0001896,"cacheRead":0.00462294,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00481254}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776487129884,"responseId":"06323ddafbb9b02ac39dc178097377cc"}}
