{"type":"message","id":"cc259dd8","parentId":"7bae5599","timestamp":"2026-04-18T04:39:04.658Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The scorer returns 0 for \"帮我写一个Python快速排序\". That's because the scoring.js Chinese patterns are weak. The user is right that I should fix the scoring patterns instead of making the user test.\n\nLet me directly improve the scoring.js to better handle Chinese task descriptions. The issue is that the scoring rules are mostly in English and don't catch Chinese patterns like \"写一个\", \"帮我\", \"分析\", \"生成\" etc.","thinkingSignature":"11360105843cff1f5cead75e468d1308570b7b9d06a47d396ced129ab5265ff2"},{"type":"text","text":"scorer 对中文返回 0——这是根本问题。hook 再好使，scorer 打不出分也白搭。\n\n**我直接修 scoring.js 的中文 pattern**：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1xhfyxmbyzg9_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/scoring.js","offset":1,"limit":80}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":55409,"output":185,"cacheRead":21865,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77459,"cost":{"input":0.0166227,"output":0.000222,"cacheRead":0.0013119,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.018156600000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776487138054,"responseId":"06323de1394ba209479196b09ed9d835"}}
{"type":"message","id":"82b31ae4","parentId":"cc259dd8","timestamp":"2026-04-18T04:39:05.090Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_1xhfyxmbyzg9_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/**\n * OpenClaw v8.0 独立评分引擎\n * 6因子 + 平方根归一化 + 特殊规则\n * 替代 v7 依赖，生产就绪\n */\n\n// ============================================================================\n// 因子定义 (6个维度，每个0-3分)\n// ============================================================================\n\nconst FACTOR_DEFINITIONS = {\n // 逻辑复杂度：重构、算法、多文件等\n logic: {\n max: 3,\n patterns: [\n { weight: 2, regex: /重构|refactor|重写|rewrite|重新设计|redesign/ },\n { weight: 2, regex: /抽象|abstract|架构|architecture|模块化|modularize/ },\n { weight: 2, regex: /递归|recursion|算法优化|algorithm|复杂度|complexity/ },\n { weight: 1, regex: /多个文件|多文件|multi[ -]file|跨模块|cross[ -]module/ },\n { weight: 1, regex: /条件分支|if[ -]else|switch|循环|loop|嵌套|nested/ },\n { weight: 1, regex: /正则|regex|状态机|state machine/ },\n ]\n },\n\n // 风险度：删除、数据库、系统修改等\n risk: {\n max: 3,\n patterns: [\n { weight: 3, regex: /删除|delete|rm|remove|清空|clear|销毁|destroy|卸载|uninstall/ },\n { weight: 3, regex: /数据库|database|drop|truncate|迁移|migration|备份|backup/ },\n { weight: 2, regex: /修改权限|chmod|chown|sudo|root|系统|system|内核|kernel/ },\n { weight: 2, regex: /生产环境|production|线上|敏感|secret|token|密码|password/ },\n { weight: 1, regex: /覆盖|overwrite|强制|force|批量|batch|递归删除|recursive delete/ },\n { weight: 1, regex: /网络请求|curl|wget|下载|download|上传|upload/ },\n ]\n },\n\n // 预估时长：编译、安装、测试等\n duration: {\n max: 3,\n patterns: [\n { weight: 3, regex: /编译|compile|构建|build|打包|package|bundle/ },\n { weight: 3, regex: /安装.*依赖|install.*dep|npm install|yarn add|pip install|cargo build|go mod/ },\n { weight: 2, regex: /测试|test|运行测试|run test|覆盖率|coverage/ },\n { weight: 2, regex: /下载|download|拉取|fetch|clone|克隆/ },\n { weight: 1, regex: /扫描|scan|分析|analyze|检查|check|lint/ },\n { weight: 1, regex: /大量文件|large|许多|many|全部|all/ },\n ]\n },\n\n // 资源消耗：GPU、视频、大数据等\n resource: {\n max: 3,\n patterns: [\n { weight: 3, regex: /训练|train|模型|model|推理|inference|GPU|CUDA/ },\n { weight: 2, regex: /视频|video|图像|image|处理|process|转换|convert/ },\n { weight: 2, regex: /大数据|big data|GB|TB|日志|log|海量|massive/ },\n { weight: 1, regex: /多进程|parallel|并发|concurrent|多线程|thread/ },\n { weight: 1, regex: /索引|index|压缩|compress|解压|extract/ },\n ]\n },\n\n // 不确定性：API调用、网络、调试等\n uncertainty: {\n max: 3,\n patterns: [\n { weight: 3, regex: /API|接口|请求|request|响应|response|HTTP/ },\n { weight: 2, regex: /外部|external|第三方|third[ -]party|依赖服务|service/ },\n { weight: 2, regex: /网络|network|连接|connect|超时|timeout|重试|retry/ },\n { weight: 1, regex: /可能|maybe|或许|尝试|try|探索|explore|不确定|uncertain/ },\n { weight: 1, regex: /调试|debug|排查|troubleshoot|修复|fix/ },\n ]\n },\n\n // 依赖复杂度：monorepo、微服务、多依赖等\n dependency: {\n max: 3,\n patterns: [\n { weight: 3, regex: /monorepo|多包|workspace|工作区|子项目|submodule/ },\n { weight: 2, regex: /多个依赖|多依赖|依赖关系|dependency graph/ },\n\n[190 more lines in file. Use offset=81 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776487145005}}
{"type":"message","id":"e8367b66","parentId":"82b31ae4","timestamp":"2026-04-18T04:39:10.077Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the scoring.js has English patterns. I need to also check the Chinese patterns. Let me read the rest of the file.","thinkingSignature":"2a2352afcc81b46d9b93e76376654f77828a9a07e3ec83df31a956d1f75861bf"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ijq3acx9dupj_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/scoring.js","offset":81,"limit":120}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":56623,"output":87,"cacheRead":21865,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78575,"cost":{"input":0.0169869,"output":0.00010439999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0013119,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0184032}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776487145092,"responseId":"06323de796afb96193c24965700e1829"}}
{"type":"message","id":"abff3253","parentId":"e8367b66","timestamp":"2026-04-18T04:39:10.516Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ijq3acx9dupj_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":" { weight: 2, regex: /微服务|microservice|服务网格|service mesh/ },\n { weight: 1, regex: /第三方库|library|框架|framework|插件|plugin/ },\n { weight: 1, regex: /前后端|frontend.*backend|全栈|full[ -]stack/ },\n ]\n }\n};\n\n// ============================================================================\n// 辅助函数\n// ============================================================================\n\n/**\n * 计算单个因子的原始分数 (0-max)\n */\nfunction calculateFactorScore(text, context, factorDef) {\n let score = 0;\n const lowerText = text.toLowerCase();\n\n for (const pattern of factorDef.patterns) {\n if (pattern.regex.test(lowerText)) {\n score = Math.max(score, pattern.weight);\n }\n }\n\n // 上下文增强\n if (factorDef === FACTOR_DEFINITIONS.logic && context.fileCount > 10) {\n score = Math.max(score, 2);\n }\n if (factorDef === FACTOR_DEFINITIONS.duration && context.estimatedLines > 1000) {\n score = Math.max(score, 2);\n }\n if (factorDef === FACTOR_DEFINITIONS.risk && context.isProduction) {\n score = Math.max(score, 2);\n }\n\n return Math.min(score, factorDef.max);\n}\n\n/**\n * 平方根归一化：原始分数 (0-18) → 0-100\n * 曲线特点：低分增长快，高分增长缓，更符合实际分布\n */\nfunction normalizeScore(rawScore) {\n // rawScore 范围 0-18\n // 公式：sqrt(rawScore / 18) * 100\n // 0→0, 2→33, 3→41, 6→57, 9→70, 12→81, 18→100\n const normalized = Math.round(Math.sqrt(rawScore / 18) * 100);\n return Math.min(100, normalized);\n}\n\n/**\n * 策略选择 (基于归一化分数和特殊规则)\n */\nfunction selectStrategy(normalizedScore, factors) {\n // 特殊规则 1：高风险强制隔离执行\n if (factors.risk >= 3) {\n return { strategy: 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT', timeout: 180 };\n }\n\n // 特殊规则 2：高资源消耗强制并行分片\n if (factors.resource >= 3) {\n return { strategy: 'PARALLEL_SHARDS', timeout: 300 };\n }\n\n // 特殊规则 3：高不确定性强制隔离\n if (factors.uncertainty >= 3) {\n return { strategy: 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT', timeout: 180 };\n }\n\n // === 组合规则：识别隐含的巨型任务 ===\n // 长耗时 + 复杂依赖 → MEGA_TASK\n if (factors.duration >= 3 && factors.dependency >= 2) {\n return { strategy: 'MEGA_TASK', timeout: 7200 };\n }\n // 高逻辑 + 长耗时 → 至少 PARALLEL_SHARDS\n if (factors.logic >= 3 && factors.duration >= 3) {\n return { strategy: 'PARALLEL_SHARDS', timeout: 300 };\n }\n\n // 标准分数区间\n if (normalizedScore <= 20) {\n return { strategy: 'DIRECT', timeout: 30 };\n } else if (normalizedScore <= 40) {\n return { strategy: 'STEP_ARCHIVE', timeout: 60 };\n } else if (normalizedScore <= 60) {\n return { strategy: 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT', timeout: 120 };\n } else if (normalizedScore <= 80) {\n return { strategy: 'PARALLEL_SHARDS', timeout: 240 };\n } else {\n return { strategy: 'MEGA_TASK', timeout: 7200 };\n }\n}\n\n// ============================================================================\n// 公开 API\n// ============================================================================\n\n/**\n * 主评分函数\n * @param {string} prompt - 用户输入的任务描述\n * @param {Object} context - 可选的上下文信息 (fileCount, estimatedLines, isProduction)\n * @returns {Object} { score, factors, recommendedStrategy, timeout }\n */\nfunction scoreTask(prompt, context = {}) {\n const text = prompt || '';\n const factors = {};\n let rawTotal = 0;\n\n // 计算各因子原始分数\n for (const [name, def] of Object.entries(FACTOR_DEFINITIONS)) {\n const factorScore = calculateFactorScore(text, context, def);\n factors[name] = factorScore;\n rawTotal += factorScore;\n }\n\n // 归一化到 0-100\n const normalizedScore = normalizeScore(rawTotal);\n\n // 选择策略和超时\n const { strategy, timeout } = selectStrategy(normalizedScore, factors);\n\n[70 more lines in file. Use offset=201 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776487150427}}
{"type":"message","id":"e8f9f168","parentId":"abff3253","timestamp":"2026-04-18T04:39:22.683Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the issue now. The `calculateFactorScore` function does `text.toLowerCase()` and then tests regex patterns that are in English. But the Chinese characters ARE lowercased by `.toLowerCase()` (though Chinese doesn't change case). The regex patterns like `/重构|refactor|重写/` should work for Chinese.\n\nLet me check: the issue is that `toLowerCase()` on Chinese text doesn't change anything, and the regex tests should work. Let me test why \"帮我写一个Python快速排序\" gets 0.\n\nLooking at the patterns:\n- logic: patterns for 重构, 抽象, 架构, 递归, 算法... but \"快速排序\" (quicksort) should match \"算法\" in some way. But the pattern is `算法优化|algorithm` which is \"算法优化\" specifically, not just \"算法\". And there's no \"排序\" or \"算法\" in the logic patterns.\n\n\n- The Chinese patterns exist but they're specific like `算法优化`, not general enough. And `快速排序` alone doesn't match any pattern since it's a specific algorithm implementation that doesn't trigger the optimization-related regex. The risk, duration, and resource patterns also don't match anything in the user input, so everything scores 0.\n\nThe fix is to add more general Chinese task keywords like 写, 创建, 生成, 分析, 实现 to the logic category, and broaden the algorithm patterns to include 排序, 查找, 图论. I should also add specific patterns for code generation tasks.","thinkingSignature":"8d5af765a117e91b0959a8cf8f5067d7fe6423c0bc45c146c844e08bf1d40cd0"},{"type":"text","text":"问题在 scoring.js 的 pattern 覆盖不够。把中文关键词 pattern 补强：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_16gde4f7x56e_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/scoring.js","offset":201}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":57700,"output":376,"cacheRead":21865,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79941,"cost":{"input":0.01731,"output":0.00045119999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0013119,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0190731}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776487150519,"responseId":"06323decf9ae3ce682da62737629e736"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f1e6f282","parentId":"e8f9f168","timestamp":"2026-04-18T04:39:23.186Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_16gde4f7x56e_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n return {\n score: normalizedScore,\n factors,\n recommendedStrategy: strategy,\n timeout,\n // 附加原始总分供调试\n _raw: { total: rawTotal, max: 18 }\n };\n}\n\n/**\n * 快速评分 (兼容旧接口)\n */\nfunction quickScore(prompt, context = {}) {\n const result = scoreTask(prompt, context);\n return {\n totalScore: result.score,\n factors: result.factors,\n strategy: result.recommendedStrategy,\n timeout: result.timeout\n };\n}\n\n/**\n * 意图检测：判断是任务还是闲聊\n */\nfunction detectIntent(prompt) {\n const taskPatterns = [\n /运行|执行|run|exec|构建|build|测试|test|部署|deploy/,\n /编译|compile|打包|package|安装|install|配置|config/,\n /创建|create|生成|generate|删除|delete|修改|modify|更新|update/,\n /分析|analyze|检查|check|修复|fix|重构|refactor/,\n /帮我|help|请|please|做|do|写|write/,\n ];\n\n const chatPatterns = [\n /你好|hello|hi|嘿|在吗|怎么样|如何|什么是|what is/,\n /解释|explain|介绍|introduce|谢谢|thanks|再见|bye/,\n /天气|weather|时间|time|日期|date/,\n ];\n\n const text = prompt.toLowerCase();\n\n for (const pattern of taskPatterns) {\n if (pattern.test(text)) {\n return { intent: 'task', confidence: 0.8 };\n }\n }\n for (const pattern of chatPatterns) {\n if (pattern.test(text)) {\n return { intent: 'chat', confidence: 0.8 };\n }\n }\n\n // 默认按任务处理\n return { intent: 'task', confidence: 0.5 };\n}\n\n// ============================================================================\n// 导出\n// ============================================================================\n\nmodule.exports = {\n scoreTask,\n quickScore,\n detectIntent,\n // 导出因子定义供外部调优\n FACTOR_DEFINITIONS\n};"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776487163061}}
{"type":"message","id":"d0237c0f","parentId":"f1e6f282","timestamp":"2026-04-18T04:39:43.463Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the full scoring.js. The issue is clear: the patterns are too specific. For example:\n\n- `logic`: 重构, 抽象, 架构, 算法优化 - doesn't cover general task descriptions\n- The Chinese patterns for task detection exist in `detectIntent` but aren't used in the actual scoring\n\nThe fix: I need to add more general patterns to each factor, especially:\n1. Logic: Add patterns for 写代码, 生成代码, 实现, 排序, 查找, 树, 图, 遍历\n2. Duration: Add patterns for 生成文档, 写报告, 分析报告\n\n\n3. Add a new factor or enhance existing ones to capture \"帮我做X\" type tasks\n\nI should make these changes carefully and conservatively. The core issue is that `calculateFactorScore` uses `text.toLowerCase()` but the regex patterns are mixed case-insensitive patterns, so Chinese characters pass through unchanged and ASCII gets lowercased, which should work fine. But the real problem is the patterns themselves are too narrow—they need to be expanded to catch the broader range of task descriptions.\n\nI'll add patterns for things like \"写一个Python快速排序\" to the logic factor, and broaden \"算法优化\" to just \"算法\" since quicksort is fundamentally an algorithm.","thinkingSignature":"d9e60a9f2c4e103c07f15c564a65b5f57ba7865d34f48de67553d47cadc84d3c"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了。pattern 太细，`\"写一个Python快速排序\"` 没有任何一个 pattern 能匹配。直接在 logic factor 里加通用编程任务词：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_px4vrloe6394_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/scoring.js","edits":[{"oldText":" logic: {\n max: 3,\n patterns: [\n { weight: 2, regex: /重构|refactor|重写|rewrite|重新设计|redesign/ },\n { weight: 2, regex: /抽象|abstract|架构|architecture|模块化|modularize/ },\n { weight: 2, regex: /递归|recursion|算法优化|algorithm|复杂度|complexity/ },\n { weight: 1, regex: /多个文件|多文件|multi[ -]file|跨模块|cross[ -]module/ },\n { weight: 1, regex: /条件分支|if[ -]else|switc