{"type":"message","id":"743e4cbf","parentId":"ad397b40","timestamp":"2026-04-18T08:43:44.669Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Hook is working and calling scorer (and getting connection refused), but the scorer is dead. The hook v10 is loaded correctly (SCORER_ERROR means it's calling scorer but getting refused, which means the hook code is working - it's reaching the scorer call). \n\nThe problem: 3103 scorer is dead. The service died at some point after 12:54 and hasn't been restarted.\n\nI need to:\n1. Start the scorer (3103)\n2. Start the context-api (3101)\n\nThen everything should work again. The hook will automatically retry on next message.\n\nThe system is actually mostly working - the hook is doing its job correctly (calling scorer, getting refused, falling back to normal). \n\nNow I'll just restart the services and get them back up.","thinkingSignature":"0cf58250822ae9503f49e632c36d76a62f8d7509e32b43efc928c434a72fea26"},{"type":"text","text":"Hook 一直在正常工作，只是 scorer 挂了。重启服务：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_879usuvt7r6y_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"bash /tmp/fix-all.sh"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":78293,"output":200,"cacheRead":21865,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100358,"cost":{"input":0.0234879,"output":0.00023999999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0013119,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0250398}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776501812202,"responseId":"0632773204cf3fe26f78f402d9fc60cf"}}
