{"type":"message","id":"e6d39d92","parentId":"34dac91e","timestamp":"2026-04-18T08:43:57.257Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All services are up and running now:\n- 3103 scorer: working (score=41 for quick sort)\n- 3101 context-api: working\n- 3105 classifier: running\n- Gateway: running\n\nNow let me report the situation to the user.","thinkingSignature":"189332481b9e8e689ee075e3e21c42030b4887a82d28c81302361ace12b6573e"},{"type":"text","text":"全部恢复：\n\n| 服务 | 状态 | 备注 |\n|------|------|------|\n| Gateway | ✅ PID 15354 | 正常运行 |\n| 3103 Scorer | ✅ PID 38708 | 评分正常（快速排序=41） |\n| 3101 Context API | ✅ PID 38711 | 健康 |\n| 3105 Classifier | ✅ 运行中 | — |\n\n**原因**：scorer 和 context-api 在我上次频繁重启之间挂了，bot 后台没能自动拉起。但 hook 的降级逻辑正确——scorer 不可用时自动回退到主 agent 处理，没有把系统搞坏。\n\n**下次应该做的事**：把 scorer 和 context-api 注册成 systemd user service，防止崩溃后无人管。我现在做吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":78843,"output":215,"cacheRead":21865,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100923,"cost":{"input":0.023652899999999998,"output":0.000258,"cacheRead":0.0013119,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0252228}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776501829131,"responseId":"06327744ee419066dcc0f6c52785fc1a"}}
