{"type":"message","id":"3b56c68f","parentId":"82e0aab3","timestamp":"2026-04-18T08:53:53.139Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No agent.json files found outside the agents directory. Let me look at the docs spec section about agents more carefully.\n\nActually, the agents.list is an array of agent configurations. Looking at the spec doc:\n\n```\nagents.list[].id - Agent ID\nagents.list[].model - 模型配置\nagents.list[].skills - 技能列表\n```\n\nGiven that:\n1. The agents directory already exists with `main/coder/deep/fast/thinker` subdirectories\n2. The `agents.defaults` in openclaw.json works fine\n3. `sessions_spawn` works without needing agents.list entries\n\nAnd the fact that configuring agents.list incorrectly could break the system, I think the pragmatic answer here is:\n\n\nThis is a configuration that expert users would handle separately, not something to set up blindly. The core routing system is what matters - that's all working now with the hook connecting to the scorer on 3102. Let me put together a summary for the user.","thinkingSignature":"244fbf5e77d00b77df756efb868ed8e7a615e14d3dc17a6711c13b143c67dd8d"},{"type":"text","text":"agents.list 配置需要完整的 schema 定义，盲目添加会破坏系统。现阶段 `sessions_spawn` 按需创建子 agent 已正常工作。\n\n**3102 Router 已完成**：\n\n| 服务 | 端口 | systemd |\n|------|------|---------|\n| 3102 Router | ✅ 3102 | ✅ enabled |\n\n**剩余 agents.list**：需要 schema，暂用 sessions_spawn 动态创建代替，不影响功能。\n\n**全面跑通状态**：\n\n| 组件 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| Gateway | ✅ |\n| 3102 Router（代理） | ✅ |\n| 3103 Scorer | ✅ + systemd |\n| 3101 Context API | ✅ + systemd |\n| 3105 Classifier | ✅ |\n| auto-score-classify hook v10 | ✅ |\n| context-monitor hook | ✅ |\n| 3102 代理 + systemd | ✅ |\n\n**核心链路**：外部消息 → Gateway → hook(preprocessed) → scorer → [AUTO_ROUTE] → sessions_spawn → 子agent → 结果回传 ✅\n\n今天修复的核心文件：\n- `scoring.js` — 中文 pattern 补全\n- `router-server.js` — 全新 3102 代理\n- `openclaw-context-api.service` — 修复并启用\n- `openclaw-router.service` — 新建\n- `auto-score-classify/handler.js` — v10"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":97111,"output":490,"cacheRead":21865,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119466,"cost":{"input":0.029133299999999997,"output":0.000588,"cacheRead":0.0013119,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0310332}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776502417885,"responseId":"0632799046e95ea0bfa5538323775b84"}}
