{"type":"message","id":"7c5607ff","parentId":"9d02e91f","timestamp":"2026-04-18T09:09:02.287Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"3108 is not running. Let me check what it is supposed to be. Looking at the architecture doc, 3105 is the Classifier, but the document also mentions \"3108\" somewhere. Let me search for more info about 3108.Actually, looking at the summary context from earlier: \"3105 Classifier 返回 scene: 'clarify' 置信度低，hook 依赖 3103 scorer 为主要评分依据，3105 作为 scene 参考\"\n\nAnd in the architecture.md, 3105 is the v8 Classifier. \n\nThe 3108 port might be referenced in the spec as scene-classifier. Let me search for what's supposed to be on 3108. Maybe it's the \"middleware router\" that the spec mentions.\n\n\nSo the v8 Router on 3102 is the internal microservice routing layer that houses both the 3103 Scorer and 3105 Classifier. The 3108 port appears to be an alternative or legacy reference to the same scene-classifier functionality. I need to find the scene-classifier service in the workspace skills to understand what's actually running on that port.","thinkingSignature":"dd90f1c6b788dee7d3128388c437c491ccbb5119172d627ea64299d9a8895844"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jfmoot8aa1y5_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/ | grep -E \"scene|classifier\"\nls ~/.openclaw/skills/ | grep -E \"scene|classifier\"\necho \"---\"\ncat ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/v8_classifier/SKILL.md 2>/dev/null | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":103966,"output":314,"cacheRead":21865,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126145,"cost":{"input":0.0311898,"output":0.0003768,"cacheRead":0.0013119,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0328785}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776503334584,"responseId":"06327d244a0d92556bb477d41406fb6a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"485567c7","parentId":"7c5607ff","timestamp":"2026-04-18T09:09:02.790Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_jfmoot8aa1y5_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"classifier-health\nscene-classifier\nv8_classifier\nv8_classifier\n---\n---\nname: v8_classifier\ndescription: OpenClaw v8 场景分类器。调用 3105 API，将用户消息分类为9种意图场景（闲聊/任务/故障/模糊等）。用于理解用户消息的底层意图，配合 v8_scorer 做路由决策。\nversion: 2.0.0\n---\n\n# v8_classifier\n\n> OpenClaw v8 场景分类器（端口 3105）\n>\n> 基于嵌入向量 + KNN 分类，规则兜底，Pipeline 统一封装\n\n---\n\n## 一、分类原理\n\n### 1.1 两层分类器架构\n\n**第一层：embedding 分类器**（主用）\n- 模型：`paraphrase-multilingual-MiniLM-L12-v2`（sentence-transformers，约 120MB，多语言支持）"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":256,"aggregated":"classifier-health\nscene-classifier\nv8_classifier\nv8_classifier\n---\n---\nname: v8_classifier\ndescription: OpenClaw v8 场景分类器。调用 3105 API，将用户消息分类为9种意图场景（闲聊/任务/故障/模糊等）。用于理解用户消息的底层意图，配合 v8_scorer 做路由决策。\nversion: 2.0.0\n---\n\n# v8_classifier\n\n> OpenClaw v8 场景分类器（端口 3105）\n>\n> 基于嵌入向量 + KNN 分类，规则兜底，Pipeline 统一封装\n\n---\n\n## 一、分类原理\n\n### 1.1 两层分类器架构\n\n**第一层：embedding 分类器**（主用）\n- 模型：`paraphrase-multilingual-MiniLM-L12-v2`（sentence-transformers，约 120MB，多语言支持）","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776503342710}}
{"type":"message","id":"bc9d578d","parentId":"485567c7","timestamp":"2026-04-18T09:09:08.091Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the v8_classifier skill calls 3105 for scene classification. The 3105 is already running (as confirmed earlier). \n\nLet me check if there's a separate scene-classifier service that should be on 3108. The classifier-health skill might give a clue.","thinkingSignature":"b112273599d54777109c05ca56c84a3ecaa46f16f8069d3f1bc20ecf4e9121e7"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_58zxz4nqr8e0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier/SKILL.md 2>/dev/null | head -30\necho \"---\"\ncat ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/classifier-health/SKILL.md 2>/dev/null | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":104486,"output":135,"cacheRead":21865,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126486,"cost":{"input":0.0313458,"output":0.00016199999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0013119,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0328197}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776503342793,"responseId":"06327d2ecbd9e1c3685ed567e5db4803"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5c1caf8e","parentId":"bc9d578d","timestamp":"2026-04-18T09:09:08.721Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_58zxz4nqr8e0_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Scene Classifier - 场景分类器\n\n> 基于嵌入向量的轻量级场景分类系统\n\n## 模块结构\n\n```\nscene-classifier/\n├── SKILL.md                      # 本文件\n├── __init__.py                   # 主入口\n├── pipeline.py                   # Pipeline 编排器\n├── data/\n│   └── synthetic_training_data.py   # 训练数据构造\n├── classifier/\n│   └── scene_classifier.py          # 分类器模型\n├── templates/\n│   └── template_map.py               # 模板注入\n├── scripts/\n│   └── train_classifier.py           # 训练脚本\n└── feedback/\n    └── collector.py                  # 反馈收集\n```\n\n## 功能\n\n| 模块 | 功能 |\n|------|------|\n| **硬拦截层** | CRITICAL 风险直接拦截，不经过 LLM |\n| **场景分类器** | 基于 sentence-transformers 嵌入 + KNN |\n| **模板注入** | 根据场景自动填充回复模板 |\n---\n---\nname: classifier-health\ndescription: 分类器健康检查与自动恢复机制，包含服务健康检测、自动重连、熔断降级。触发词：分类服务健康检查、熔断、自动重连。\n---\n\n# Classifier Health - 分类器健康检查\n\n## 功能\n\n为 classifierClient.js 添加稳定性保障：\n- 定期健康检查（30秒间隔）\n- 自动重连逻辑（最多3次）\n- 熔断机制（连续3次失败后降级）\n- 规则分类器降级方案\n\n## 触发词\n\n- 分类服务挂了、分类服务不可用\n- 健康检查、重连、熔断\n- 分类器降级"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":242,"aggregated":"# Scene Classifier - 场景分类器\n\n> 基于嵌入向量的轻量级场景分类系统\n\n## 模块结构\n\n```\nscene-classifier/\n├── SKILL.md                      # 本文件\n├── __init__.py                   # 主入口\n├── pipeline.py                   # Pipeline 编排器\n├── data/\n│   └── synthetic_training_data.py   # 训练数据构造\n├── classifier/\n│   └── scene_classifier.py          # 分类器模型\n├── templates/\n│   └── template_map.py               # 模板注入\n├── scripts/\n│   └── train_classifier.py           # 训练脚本\n└── feedback/\n    └── collector.py                  # 反馈收集\n```\n\n## 功能\n\n| 模块 | 功能 |\n|------|------|\n| **硬拦截层** | CRITICAL 风险直接拦截，不经过 LLM |\n| **场景分类器** | 基于 sentence-transformers 嵌入 + KNN |\n| **模板注入** | 根据场景自动填充回复模板 |\n---\n---\nname: classifier-health\ndescription: 分类器健康检查与自动恢复机制，包含服务健康检测、自动重连、熔断降级。触发词：分类服务健康检查、熔断、自动重连。\n---\n\n# Classifier Health - 分类器健康检查\n\n## 功能\n\n为 classifierClient.js 添加稳定性保障：\n- 定期健康检查（30秒间隔）\n- 自动重连逻辑（最多3次）\n- 熔断机制（连续3次失败后降级）\n- 规则分类器降级方案\n\n## 触发词\n\n- 分类服务挂了、分类服务不可用\n- 健康检查、重连、熔断\n- 分类器降级","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776503348635}}
{"type":"message","id":"6750a0e5","parentId":"5c1caf8e","timestamp":"2026-04-18T09:09:18.280Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The scene-classifier is a Python skill, not a separate service on port 3108. The 3105 is the actual classification service. \n\nThe 3108 reference in the spec might be outdated or it could be that the spec writer numbered it differently. The key is that 3105 IS running.\n\nLet me focus on what's actually missing:\n1. ✅ context-monitor HOOK.md - already has `---` \n2. ✅ context-monitor hook - 7 handlers loaded, no errors\n3. auto-router - no handler\n4. 3108 - might not be relevant if 3105 is the classifier\n\n\n5. Now I need to track down what's actually consuming resources on the system.","thinkingSignature":"2575927404c9a913de94b47cca7336221861919ee5319c573b8abaf8a2527684"},{"type":"text","text":"3105 已经在运行。scene-classifier 是 Python skill，3105 是它的服务端口。3108 在当前环境里不是关键问题。\n\n**真正需要修复的**：\n1. ✅ context-monitor — HOOK.md 有 `---`，7 handlers 无报错\n2. ❌ auto-router — 无 handler，只有文档\n\n先确认 context-monitor 真的在工作：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_krq9zz7v7al0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep \"context-monitor\\]\" /tmp/openclaw/openclaw-2026-04-18.log | tail -5"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":104977,"output":272,"cacheRead":21865,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127114,"cost":{"input":0.031493099999999996,"output":0.00032639999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0013119,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03313139999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776503348724,"responseId":"06327d344571c782161585a5e5e4a674"}}
