{"type":"message","id":"dffaa5ee","parentId":"4a8fd68e","timestamp":"2026-04-18T09:46:05.992Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see some issues:\n\n1. The ephemeral shows `[AUTO_ROUTE]` messages being scored. That means the hook is scoring messages that ALREADY have the [AUTO_ROUTE] prefix - it's double-processing them! When auto-score-classify injects `[AUTO_ROUTE]`, the resulting message gets re-scored in the next turn, potentially with the same score.\n\n2. There's a HEARTBEAT poll that scored 41 (SPAWN_SUBAGENT) - that's wrong. Heartbeats should NOT be scored and should NOT trigger AUTO_ROUTE. This means heartbeats are going through the hook and being scored, which could cause unintended subagent spawns.\n\n\n3. The HEARTBEAT check at 17:27:45 was scored 41 and INJECTED [AUTO_ROUTE], which would have spawned a subagent. But the HEARTBEAT at 17:27 was actually my NO_REPLY response - so the hook is processing my own responses and spawning subagents unnecessarily. This is a critical bug.\n\nLet me look more closely at what's happening: at 17:27:45, a heartbeat poll with the content \"Read HEARTBEAT.md...\" was scored 41 and injected with [AUTO_ROUTE], causing a subagent spawn. But then at 17:45:12, another message was scored 24 and skipped, and the ephemeral shows a \"[AUTO_ROUTE]\" message starting to appear.\n\nThe core issue is that the hook's early return check for `[AUTO_ROUTE]` doesn't work because by the time auto-score-classify injects the prefix, the message has already been scored and written to ephemeral without it. When the same message gets scored again in the next turn, it finally has the prefix and gets skipped, but by then the ephemeral has a duplicate entry without it. More critically, heartbeat polls are being scored and triggering subagent spawns when they should be filtered out before scoring ever happens.\n\nI need to add a heartbeat filter at the start of the handler to catch messages like \"HEARTBEAT_OK\", \"Read HEARTBEAT.md\", and other poll patterns before they reach the scoring logic.","thinkingSignature":"6d5c7fed79cdfa5ec5a797ee3f34b8904de7b766d398fb8f712ce40413c15026"},{"type":"text","text":"**发现严重问题**：ephemeral 数据显示 `[AUTO_ROUTE]` 消息被重复评分，且 HEARTBEAT 被当作任务触发派发。\n\n这是两个真实 bug：\n\n1. **HEARTBEAT 触发派发**：17:27 的心跳得分 41 → `INJECTED [AUTO_ROUTE]` → 不该 spawn 的心跳也 spawn 了\n2. **重复评分**：`[AUTO_ROUTE]` 消息在下一个 turn 被重新评分\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_h5411gjeg5xc_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== HEARTBEAT 相关 INJECTED ===\"\ngrep \"HEARTBEAT\\|INJECTED\" /tmp/openclaw/openclaw-2026-04-18.log | grep \"INJECTED\" | tail -5"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":119077,"output":621,"cacheRead":21865,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":141563,"cost":{"input":0.0357231,"output":0.0007452,"cacheRead":0.0013119,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0377802}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776505546757,"responseId":"063285caf6a763031d741fe9a87e47a2"}}
